msgstr ""
"Saat tombol :guilabel:`New` diklik dalam tampilan Kanban default pada "
"halaman :guilabel:`Campaigns`, kartu Kanban muncul di tahapan "
":guilabel:`New`."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/email_marketing.rst:None
msgid "View of the campaign pop-up kanban in Odoo Email Marketing."
msgstr "Tampilan pop-up kanban kampanye di Odoo Email Marketing."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/email_marketing.rst:718
msgid ""
"New campaign cards can also be made by clicking the :guilabel:`➕ (plus "
