msgstr ":doc:`../marketing_automation`"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/email_marketing/mailing_lists.rst:5
msgid ""
"Mailing lists in Odoo are used for both pre and post sales communications in "
"the *Email Marketing* application. They provide sales teams with qualified "
"lead lists, focus group participants, or current customers that fulfill "
"specific criteria."
msgstr ""
"Daftar mailing di Odoo digunakan untuk komunikasi pra dan pasca penjualan di "
"aplikasi *Email Marketing*. Daftar ini menyediakan tim Penjualan dengan "
"daftar prospek yang memenuhi syarat, peserta kelompok fokus, atau pelanggan "
"saat ini yang memenuhi kriteria tertentu."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/email_marketing/mailing_lists.rst:9
msgid ""
"Mailing lists can be generated in Odoo, and exported as a downloadable file, "
"or into the *Knowledge*, *Dashboards*, or *Spreadsheets* applications, or "
"imported via copy/paste or file upload."
msgstr ""
"Daftar mailing dapat dibuat di Odoo, dan diekspor sebagai file yang dapat "
"diunduh, atau ke aplikasi *Pengetahuan*, *Dashboard*, atau *Spreadsheets*, "
"atau diimpor melalui salin/tempel atau unggah file."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/email_marketing/mailing_lists.rst:14
msgid "Create mailing lists"
msgstr "Buat mailing list"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/email_marketing/mailing_lists.rst:16
msgid ""
"To create a mailing list in the *Email Marketing* application, navigate "
"to :menuselection:`Email Marketing app --> Mailing Lists --> Mailing Lists --"
"> New`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk membuat daftar mailing di aplikasi *Email Marketing*, navigasikan ke "
":menuselection:`aplikasi Email Marketing --> Daftar Mailing --> Daftar "
"Mailing --> Baru`."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/email_marketing/mailing_lists.rst:19
msgid "Clicking :guilabel:`New` reveals a blank mailing list form."
msgstr ""
"Mengklik :guilabel:`Baru` akan menampilkan formulir daftar mailing kosong."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/email_marketing/mailing_lists.rst:None
msgid "View of the mailing list form in the Odoo Email Marketing application."
msgstr "Tampilan formulir mailing list di aplikasi Email Marketing Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/email_marketing/mailing_lists.rst:25
msgid ""
"On the form, type a name in the :guilabel:`Mailing List` field at the top."
msgstr ""
"Pada formulir, ketik nama di kolom :guilabel:`Mailing List` di bagian atas."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/email_marketing/mailing_lists.rst:27
msgid ""
"If the mailing list should be accessible by recipients from the subscription "
"management page, allowing them to update their preferences, tick the box "
"next to :guilabel:`Show In Preferences`."
msgstr ""
"Jika mailing list harus dapat diakses oleh penerima dari halaman pengelolaan "
"langganan, memungkinkan mereka untuk memperbarui preferensi mereka, centang "
"kotak di samping :guilabel:`Show In Preferences`."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/email_marketing/mailing_lists.rst:30
msgid ""
"In the upper-left corner of the mailing list form, there are two "
"buttons: :guilabel:`Send Mailing` and :guilabel:`Send SMS`."
msgstr ""
"Di pojok kiri atas formulir mailing list, terdapat dua tombol: "
":guilabel:`Send Mailing` dan :guilabel:`Send SMS`."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/email_marketing/mailing_lists.rst:34
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Send SMS` button **only** appears if the *SMS Marketing* "
"application is installed."
msgstr ""
"Tombol :guilabel:`Send SMS` **hanya** muncul jika aplikasi *SMS Marketing* "
"telah diinstal."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/email_marketing/mailing_lists.rst:36
msgid ""
"Clicking :guilabel:`Send Mailing` reveals a separate page with a blank email "
"template form, which can be filled out by following steps explained in "
"the :doc:`Email Marketing doc <../email_marketing>`."
msgstr ""
"Mengklik :guilabel:`Send Mailing` menampilkan halaman terpisah dengan "
"formulir template email kosong, yang dapat diisi dengan mengikuti langkah-"
"langkah yang dijelaskan dalam :doc:`dokumen Email Marketing <../"
"email_marketing>`."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/email_marketing/mailing_lists.rst:40
msgid ""
"Clicking :guilabel:`Send SMS` reveals a separate page with a blank SMS "
"template form, which can be filled out by following steps explained in "
"the :doc:`SMS Marketing doc <../sms_marketing>`."
msgstr ""
"Mengklik :guilabel:`Send SMS` menampilkan halaman terpisah dengan formulir "
"template SMS kosong, yang dapat diisi dengan mengikuti langkah-langkah yang "
"dijelaskan dalam :doc:`dokumen SMS Marketing <../sms_marketing>`."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/email_marketing/mailing_lists.rst:44
msgid ""
"At the top of the mailing list form is a series of smart buttons that "
"display a variety of metrics related to the specific mailing list. When any "
"of the smart buttons are clicked, a separate page is revealed, showcasing "
"detailed analytics related to that particular statistic."
msgstr ""
"Di bagian atas formulir mailing list terdapat serangkaian tombol pintar yang "
"menampilkan berbagai metrik terkait mailing list tertentu. Ketika salah satu "
"tombol pintar diklik, halaman terpisah ditampilkan, menampilkan analitik "
"terperinci terkait statistik tersebut."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/email_marketing/mailing_lists.rst:48
msgid "The smart buttons available on a mailing list form are:"
msgstr "Tombol pintar yang tersedia pada formulir mailing list adalah:"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/email_marketing/mailing_lists.rst:50
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Recipients`: how many people are subscribed to the mailing list"
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Recipients`: berapa banyak orang yang berlangganan mailing list"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/email_marketing/mailing_lists.rst:51
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Mailings`: how many mailings have been sent using this mailing "
"list"
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Mailings`: berapa banyak mailing yang telah dikirim menggunakan "
"mailing list ini"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/email_marketing/mailing_lists.rst:52
msgid ""
":guilabel:`% Bounce`: percentage of mailings related to this mailing list "
"that have been bounced back"
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`% Bounce`: persentase mailing terkait mailing list ini yang "
"dikembalikan"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/email_marketing/mailing_lists.rst:54
msgid ""
":guilabel:`% Opt-out`: percentage of recipients that have opted-out of "
"mailings from this mailing list"
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`% Opt-out`: persentase penerima yang telah berhenti berlangganan "
"mailing dari mailing list ini"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/email_marketing/mailing_lists.rst:56
msgid ""
":guilabel:`% Blacklist`: percentage of recipients that have blacklisted "
"themselves from the mailing list altogether"
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`% Blacklist`: persentase penerima yang telah memasukkan diri "
"mereka ke daftar hitam dari mailing list sepenuhnya"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/email_marketing/mailing_lists.rst:59
msgid ""
"Once all the configurations on the mailing list form are complete, Odoo "
"automatically adds the new mailing list to the :guilabel:`Mailing List` page "
"in the *Email Marketing* app (:menuselection:`Email Marketing app --> "
"Mailing Lists --> Mailing Lists`)."
msgstr ""
"Setelah semua konfigurasi pada formulir mailing list selesai, Odoo secara "
"otomatis menambahkan mailing list baru ke halaman :guilabel:`Mailing List` "
"di aplikasi *Email Marketing* (:menuselection:`aplikasi Email Marketing --> "
"Mailing Lists --> Mailing Lists`)."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/email_marketing/mailing_lists.rst:64
msgid "Add contacts to mailing list"
msgstr "Tambahkan kontak ke mailing list"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/email_marketing/mailing_lists.rst:66
msgid ""
"In Odoo *Email Marketing*, there are a few different ways to add contacts to "
"a mailing list."
msgstr ""
"Di Odoo *Email Marketing*, terdapat beberapa cara berbeda untuk menambahkan "
"kontak ke mailing list."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/email_marketing/mailing_lists.rst:68
msgid ""
"From the :guilabel:`Mailing Lists` page (:menuselection:`Email Marketing --> "
"Mailing Lists --> Mailing Lists`), click the :guilabel:`Total Contacts` link "
"on the line of the desired mailing list to which contacts should be added."
msgstr ""
"Dari halaman :guilabel:`Mailing Lists` (:menuselection:`Email Marketing --> "
"Mailing Lists --> Mailing Lists`), klik tautan :guilabel:`Total Contacts` "
"pada baris mailing list yang diinginkan untuk menambahkan kontak."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/email_marketing/mailing_lists.rst:72
msgid ""
"Doing so reveals a separate :guilabel:`Mailing List Contacts` page for that "
"specific mailing list, where contacts can be created or imported, and then "
"added to the specific mailing list."
msgstr ""
"Melakukan hal ini menampilkan halaman :guilabel:`Mailing List Contacts` "
"terpisah untuk mailing list tertentu, di mana kontak dapat dibuat atau "
"diimpor, dan kemudian ditambahkan ke mailing list tertentu."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/email_marketing/mailing_lists.rst:75
msgid ""
"This same page can also be accessed by clicking the desired mailing list "
"from the :guilabel:`Mailing Lists` page, and then clicking "
"the :guilabel:`Recipients` smart button on the mailing list form."
msgstr ""
"Halaman yang sama juga dapat diakses dengan mengklik mailing list yang "
"diinginkan dari halaman :guilabel:`Mailing Lists`, lalu mengklik tombol "
"pintar :guilabel:`Recipients` pada formulir mailing list."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/email_marketing/mailing_lists.rst:78
msgid ""
"Doing so *also* reveals a separate :guilabel:`Mailing List Contacts` page "
"for that specific mailing list, where contacts can be created or imported, "
"and then added to the specific mailing list."
msgstr ""
"Melakukan hal ini *juga* menampilkan halaman :guilabel:`Mailing List "
"Contacts` terpisah untuk mailing list tertentu tersebut, di mana kontak "
"dapat dibuat atau diimpor, lalu ditambahkan ke mailing list tertentu."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/email_marketing/mailing_lists.rst:81
msgid ""
"Contacts can also be directly imported to a specific mailing list from "
"the :guilabel:`Mailing Lists` page, by clicking :guilabel:`Import Contacts` "
"to the far-right of the desired mailing list."
msgstr ""
"Kontak juga dapat langsung diimpor ke mailing list tertentu dari halaman "
":guilabel:`Mailing Lists`, dengan mengklik :guilabel:`Import Contacts` di "
"sebelah kanan mailing list yang diinginkan."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/email_marketing/mailing_lists.rst:None
msgid ""
"The import contacts button of a mailing list line in Odoo Email Marketing."
msgstr "Tombol impor kontak dari baris mailing list di Odoo Email Marketing."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/email_marketing/mailing_lists.rst:88
msgid "Doing so reveals an :guilabel:`Import Mailing Contacts` pop-up form."
msgstr ""
"Melakukan hal ini menampilkan formulir pop-up :guilabel:`Import Mailing "
"Contacts`."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/email_marketing/mailing_lists.rst:None
msgid ""
"The import mailing contacts pop-up form that appears in Odoo Email Marketing."
msgstr ""
"Formulir pop-up impor mailing kontak yang muncul di Odoo Email Marketing."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/email_marketing/mailing_lists.rst:94
msgid ""
"Here, the desired mailing list is auto-populated in the :guilabel:`Import "
"contacts in` field. Beneath that, write or paste email addresses in "
"the :guilabel:`Contact List` field."
msgstr ""
"Di sini, mailing list yang diinginkan terisi otomatis di kolom "
":guilabel:`Import contacts in`. Di bawahnya, tulis atau tempel alamat email "
"di kolom :guilabel:`Contact List`."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/email_marketing/mailing_lists.rst:97
msgid ""
"The option to import a country, company name, and more is available, via "
"the :guilabel:`Upload a file` link at the bottom of the pop-up form."
msgstr ""
"Opsi untuk mengimpor negara, nama perusahaan, dan lainnya tersedia melalui "
"tautan :guilabel:`Upload a file` di bagian bawah formulir pop-up."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/email_marketing/mailing_lists.rst:100
msgid ""
"When all contacts and configurations are complete, click :guilabel:`Import`."
msgstr "Ketika semua kontak dan konfigurasi selesai, klik :guilabel:`Import`."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/email_marketing/mailing_lists.rst:102
msgid ""
"To add contacts to a specific mailing list from a master list of all mailing "
"list contacts in the database, navigate to :menuselection:`Email Marketing "
"app --> Mailing Lists --> Mailing List Contacts`. Doing so reveals "
"the :guilabel:`Mailing List Contacts` page, featuring a list of all contacts "
"associated with every mailing list."
msgstr ""
"Untuk menambahkan kontak ke mailing list tertentu dari daftar utama semua "
"kontak mailing list di database, navigasikan ke :menuselection:`Email "
"Marketing app --> Mailing Lists --> Mailing List Contacts`. Melakukan hal "
"ini menampilkan halaman :guilabel:`Mailing List Contacts`, yang menampilkan "
"daftar semua kontak yang terkait dengan setiap mailing list."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/email_marketing/mailing_lists.rst:None
msgid "The Mailing List page in the Odoo Email Marketing application."
msgstr "Halaman Mailing List di aplikasi Odoo Email Marketing."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/email_marketing/mailing_lists.rst:111
msgid ""
"The default :guilabel:`Exclude Blacklisted Emails` filter appears in the "
"search bar."
msgstr ""
"Filter default :guilabel:`Exclude Blacklisted Emails` muncul di bilah "
"pencarian."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/email_marketing/mailing_lists.rst:113
msgid ""
"From the :guilabel:`Mailing List Contacts` page, contacts can be created and/"
"or imported, and then added to a mailing list."
msgstr ""
"Dari halaman :guilabel:`Mailing List Contacts`, kontak dapat dibuat dan/atau "
"diimpor, lalu ditambahkan ke mailing list."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/email_marketing/mailing_lists.rst:116
msgid ""
"To add an existing contact to a mailing list, select the desired contact "
"from the list on the :guilabel:`Mailing List Contacts` page to reveal their "
"contact form."
msgstr ""
"Untuk menambahkan kontak yang sudah ada ke mailing list, pilih kontak yang "
"diinginkan dari daftar di halaman :guilabel:`Mailing List Contacts` untuk "
"menampilkan formulir kontak mereka."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/email_marketing/mailing_lists.rst:119
msgid ""
"At the bottom of their contact form, click :guilabel:`Add a line` under "
"the :guilabel:`Mailing List` column, locate the desired mailing list from "
"the drop-down menu, and select it."
msgstr ""
"Di bagian bawah formulir kontak mereka, klik :guilabel:`Add a line` di bawah "
"kolom :guilabel:`Mailing List`, cari mailing list yang diinginkan dari menu "
"drop-down, dan pilih."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/email_marketing/mailing_lists.rst:None
msgid ""
"The Add a line for mailing lists on a standard contact form in Odoo Email "
"Marketing."
msgstr ""
"Add a line untuk mailing list di formulir kontak standar di Odoo Email "
"Marketing."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/email_marketing/mailing_lists.rst:127
msgid ""
"A mailing list can be created directly from a contact form, by typing the "
"name of the new mailing list in the :guilabel:`Mailing List` field. Then, "
"after a new mailing list name has been entered, two options appear on the "
"drop-down menu beneath the new mailing list name."
msgstr ""
"Mailing list dapat dibuat langsung dari formulir kontak, dengan mengetik "
"nama mailing list baru di kolom :guilabel:`Mailing List`. Kemudian, setelah "
"nama mailing list baru dimasukkan, dua opsi muncul di menu drop-down di "
"bawah nama mailing list baru."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/email_marketing/mailing_lists.rst:131
msgid ""
"From this drop-down menu, select :guilabel:`Create` to create the mailing "
"list and edit it later, or select :guilabel:`Create and edit...` to create "
"and edit the new mailing list right away."
msgstr ""
"Dari menu drop-down ini, pilih :guilabel:`Create` untuk membuat mailing list "
"dan mengeditnya nanti, atau pilih :guilabel:`Create and edit...` untuk "
"membuat dan mengedit mailing list baru segera."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/email_marketing/mailing_lists.rst:134
msgid ""
"To remove a contact from a mailing list that the contact has been added to, "
"enable the :guilabel:`Opt Out` checkbox. If the :guilabel:`Opt Out` checkbox "
"is ticked, the ability to add a :guilabel:`Reason` why the contact opted-out "
"is also available."
msgstr ""
"Untuk menghapus kontak dari mailing list yang telah ditambahkan kontak, "
"aktifkan kotak centang :guilabel:`Opt Out`. Jika kotak centang "
":guilabel:`Opt Out` dicentang, kemampuan untuk menambahkan "
":guilabel:`Reason` mengapa kontak memilih keluar juga tersedia."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/email_marketing/mailing_lists.rst:138
msgid ""
"When/if a contact *has* opted-out of a mailing list, the date they activated "
"their opt-out appears in the :guilabel:`Unsubscription Date` column on their "
"contact form."
msgstr ""
"Ketika/jika kontak *telah* memilih keluar dari mailing list, tanggal mereka "
"mengaktifkan opt-out mereka muncul di kolom :guilabel:`Unsubscription Date` "
"di formulir kontak mereka."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/email_marketing/mailing_lists.rst:141
msgid ""
"Lastly, the initial :guilabel:`Subscription Date` can be seen, as well. This "
"field is auto-populated with the date and time their subscription to the "
"mailing list has been saved."
msgstr ""
"Terakhir, :guilabel:`Subscription Date` awal juga dapat dilihat. Kolom ini "
"terisi otomatis dengan tanggal dan waktu langganan mereka ke mailing list "
"telah disimpan."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/email_marketing/mailing_lists.rst:144
msgid "Multiple mailing lists can be added to a single contact form."
msgstr "Beberapa mailing list dapat ditambahkan ke satu formulir kontak."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/email_marketing/mailing_lists.rst:146
msgid ""
"To delete any mailing list from a contact form, simply click the :guilabel:`"
"🗑️ (trash can)` icon."
msgstr ""
"Untuk menghapus mailing list dari formulir kontak, cukup klik ikon "
":guilabel:`🗑️ (tong sampah)`."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/email_marketing/mailing_lists.rst:149
msgid "Link mailing list to website"
msgstr "Menautkan mailing list ke website"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/email_marketing/mailing_lists.rst:151
msgid ""
"When a mailing list is created in the database, Odoo provides the option to "
"directly link the mailing list to the Odoo-built website (created via the "
"Odoo *Website* application)."
msgstr ""
"Ketika mailing list dibuat di database, Odoo menyediakan opsi untuk langsung "
"menautkan mailing list ke website yang dibangun dengan Odoo (dibuat melalui "
"aplikasi *Website* Odoo)."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/email_marketing/mailing_lists.rst:154
msgid ""
"To link a mailing list to a website, navigate to the front-end of the "
"website, which can be accomplished in a variety of ways throughout the "
"database. The most direct way to get to the front-end of the website is to "
"simply open the :menuselection:`Website` application from the main Odoo "
"dashboard."
msgstr ""
"Untuk menautkan mailing list ke website, navigasi ke front-end website, yang "
"dapat dilakukan dengan berbagai cara di seluruh database. Cara paling "
"langsung untuk menuju front-end website adalah dengan membuka aplikasi "
":menuselection:`Website` dari Dashboard utama Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/email_marketing/mailing_lists.rst:159
msgid ""
"Doing so reveals the designated homepage of the Odoo-built website for the "
"database."
msgstr ""
"Melakukan hal tersebut akan menampilkan homepage yang telah ditentukan dari "
"website yang dibangun dengan Odoo untuk database."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/email_marketing/mailing_lists.rst:161
msgid ""
"From the front-end of the website, click the :guilabel:`Edit` button in the "
"upper-right corner. When clicked, Odoo reveals a right-sidebar, filled with "
"drag-and-drop *building blocks*, packed with various features, options, and "
"design elements."
msgstr ""
"Dari front-end website, klik tombol :guilabel:`Edit` di sudut kanan atas. "
"Saat diklik, Odoo menampilkan sidebar kanan yang berisi *building block* "
"drag-and-drop, dilengkapi dengan berbagai fitur, opsi, dan elemen desain."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/email_marketing/mailing_lists.rst:165
msgid ""
"Next, in the search bar of the right-sidebar, search for `Newsletter`. "
"The :guilabel:`Newsletter` selection of building blocks is used to add "
"subscription fields for any mailing list onto the website."
msgstr ""
"Selanjutnya, di search bar sidebar kanan, cari `Newsletter`. Pilihan "
"building block :guilabel:`Newsletter` digunakan untuk menambahkan field "
"subscription untuk mailing list apa pun ke website."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/email_marketing/mailing_lists.rst:None
msgid ""
"View of how to quickly search for Newsletter blocks in the Odoo Website "
"application."
msgstr "Tampilan cara cepat mencari block Newsletter di aplikasi Website Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/email_marketing/mailing_lists.rst:173
msgid ""
"Doing so reveals the following building block options: :guilabel:`Newsletter "
"Block`, :guilabel:`Newsletter Popup`, and :guilabel:`Newsletter`. Any of "
"these options can be used to add subscription fields for a mailing list onto "
"the website."
msgstr ""
"Melakukan hal tersebut akan menampilkan opsi building block berikut: "
":guilabel:`Newsletter Block`, :guilabel:`Newsletter Popup`, dan "
":guilabel:`Newsletter`. Salah satu opsi ini dapat digunakan untuk "
"menambahkan field subscription untuk mailing list ke website."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/email_marketing/mailing_lists.rst:177
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Newsletter Block` option places a customizable block onto the "
"body of the website where a visitor to enter their email and click a button "
"to subscribe to a designated mailing list."
msgstr ""
"Opsi :guilabel:`Newsletter Block` menempatkan block yang dapat disesuaikan "
"di body website di mana pengunjung dapat memasukkan email mereka dan "
"mengklik tombol untuk berlangganan mailing list yang ditentukan."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/email_marketing/mailing_lists.rst:None
msgid "Sample of how a newsletter block appears on an Odoo Website."
msgstr "Contoh tampilan newsletter block di Website Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/email_marketing/mailing_lists.rst:184
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Newsletter Popup` option reveals a customizable pop-up window "
"that appears when a visitor scrolls to the specific section of the webpage "
"on which the building block is placed. When the visitor reaches the "
"designated section, a pop-up window appears, in which a visitor can enter "
"their email address, click a button, and subscribe to that predetermined "
"mailing list."
msgstr ""
"Opsi :guilabel:`Newsletter Popup` menampilkan jendela pop-up yang dapat "
"disesuaikan yang muncul ketika pengunjung menggulir ke bagian tertentu dari "
"halaman web di mana building block ditempatkan. Ketika pengunjung mencapai "
"bagian yang ditentukan, jendela pop-up muncul, di mana pengunjung dapat "
"memasukkan alamat email mereka, mengklik tombol, dan berlangganan mailing "
"list yang telah ditentukan."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/email_marketing/mailing_lists.rst:None
msgid "Sample of how a newsletter popup block appears on an Odoo Website."
msgstr "Contoh tampilan newsletter popup block di Website Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/email_marketing/mailing_lists.rst:193
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Newsletter` option provides the same functionality as the "
"other options. However, it only consists of a field for the visitor to enter "
"their email address, and a button to subscribe to the mailing list."
msgstr ""
"Opsi :guilabel:`Newsletter` menyediakan fungsi yang sama dengan opsi "
"lainnya. Namun, opsi ini hanya terdiri dari field untuk pengunjung "
"memasukkan alamat email mereka, dan tombol untuk berlangganan mailing list."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/email_marketing/mailing_lists.rst:197
msgid ""
"It is covertly designed in this fashion to be cleanly implemented into the "
"content of the webpage and/or footer."
msgstr ""
"Opsi ini dirancang secara tersembunyi dengan cara ini agar dapat "
"diimplementasikan dengan rapi ke dalam konten halaman web dan/atau footer."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/email_marketing/mailing_lists.rst:204
msgid ""
"Once the desired newsletter building block is chosen, drag-and-drop it onto "
"the body of the website. Then, select the newly-placed newsletter building "
"block to reveal its configuration options on the right-sidebar."
msgstr ""
"Setelah building block newsletter yang diinginkan dipilih, drag-and-drop ke "
"body website. Kemudian, pilih building block newsletter yang baru "
"ditempatkan untuk menampilkan opsi konfigurasinya di sidebar kanan."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/email_marketing/mailing_lists.rst:208
msgid ""
"From there, open the :guilabel:`Newsletter` drop-down menu, and select the "
"specific mailing list that should be applied to the block."
msgstr ""
"Dari sana, buka menu drop-down :guilabel:`Newsletter`, dan pilih mailing "
"list spesifik yang harus diterapkan pada block."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/email_marketing/mailing_lists.rst:None
msgid ""
"The newsletter drop-down menu in the customize sidebar that appears in Odoo "
"Website."
msgstr ""
"Menu drop-down newsletter di sidebar customize yang muncul di Website Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/email_marketing/mailing_lists.rst:215
msgid ""
"Once the desired configurations and customizations are complete, be sure to "
"click the :guilabel:`Save` button in the upper-right corner."
msgstr ""
"Setelah konfigurasi dan kustomisasi yang diinginkan selesai, pastikan untuk "
"mengklik tombol :guilabel:`Save` di sudut kanan atas."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/email_marketing/mailing_lists.rst:218
msgid ""
"Now, when a visitor enters their email address, and clicks the button to "
"subscribe, they are instantly subscribed to that pre-configured mailing "
"list. They are also added as a contact for that mailing list in Odoo *Email "
"Marketing*."
msgstr ""
"Sekarang, ketika pengunjung memasukkan alamat email mereka dan mengklik "
"tombol untuk berlangganan, mereka langsung berlangganan ke daftar mailing "
"yang telah dikonfigurasi sebelumnya. Mereka juga ditambahkan sebagai kontak "
"untuk daftar mailing tersebut di Odoo *Email Marketing*."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/email_marketing/unsubscriptions.rst:3
msgid "Manage unsubscriptions (blacklist)"
msgstr "Kelola berhenti berlangganan (daftar hitam)"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/email_marketing/unsubscriptions.rst:5
msgid ""
"Providing recipients with the power to unsubscribe from mailing lists is not "
"only a smart business practice, it's often a legal requirement. Allowing "
"recipients to unsubscribe from a mailing list establishes a sense of trust "
"and control with an audience. It also helps companies appear more genuine, "
"and less *spammy*."
msgstr ""
"Memberikan penerima kekuatan untuk berhenti berlangganan dari daftar mailing "
"bukan hanya praktik bisnis yang cerdas, tetapi sering kali merupakan "
"persyaratan hukum. Memungkinkan penerima berhenti berlangganan dari daftar "
"mailing membangun rasa kepercayaan dan kontrol dengan audiens. Ini juga "
"membantu perusahaan tampak lebih tulus dan tidak *spammy*."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/email_marketing/unsubscriptions.rst:11
msgid "Unsubscribe and blacklist"
msgstr "Berhenti berlangganan dan daftar hitam"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/email_marketing/unsubscriptions.rst:13
msgid ""
"In addition to having the option to unsubscribe from specific mailing lists, "
"the recipient can also *blacklist* themselves during the unsubscription "
"process, meaning they will not receive *any* more marketing emails from the "
"Odoo database."
msgstr ""
"Selain memiliki opsi untuk berhenti berlangganan dari daftar mailing "
"tertentu, penerima juga dapat *memasukkan diri ke daftar hitam* selama "
"proses berhenti berlangganan, yang berarti mereka tidak akan menerima email "
"pemasaran *apa pun* lagi dari database Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/email_marketing/unsubscriptions.rst:17
msgid ""
"In order to provide recipients with the ability to blacklist themselves, a "
"specific feature **must** be enabled in the *Email Marketing* application."
msgstr ""
"Agar dapat memberikan penerima kemampuan untuk memasukkan diri ke daftar "
"hitam, fitur tertentu **harus** diaktifkan di aplikasi *Email Marketing*."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/email_marketing/unsubscriptions.rst:20
msgid ""
"Navigate to :menuselection:`Email Marketing app --> Configuration --> "
"Settings`, and tick the checkbox next to the :guilabel:`Blacklist Option "
"when Unsubscribing` feature. Then, click :guilabel:`Save` in the upper-left "
"corner of the :guilabel:`Settings` page."
msgstr ""
"Buka :menuselection:`Aplikasi Email Marketing --> Konfigurasi --> "
"Pengaturan`, dan centang kotak di samping fitur :guilabel:`Opsi Daftar Hitam "
"saat Berhenti Berlangganan`. Kemudian, klik :guilabel:`Simpan` di pojok kiri "
"atas halaman :guilabel:`Pengaturan`."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/email_marketing/unsubscriptions.rst:None
msgid ""
"View of the blacklist feature in the Settings page of the Odoo Email "
"Marketing app."
msgstr ""
"Tampilan fitur daftar hitam di halaman Pengaturan aplikasi Odoo Email "
"Marketing."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/email_marketing/unsubscriptions.rst:29
msgid "Unsubscribe"
msgstr "Berhenti Subskripsi"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/email_marketing/unsubscriptions.rst:31
msgid ""
"By default, an *Unsubscribe* link appears at the bottom of all mailing "
"templates."
msgstr ""
"Secara default, tautan *Berhenti Berlangganan* muncul di bagian bawah semua "
"template mailing."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/email_marketing/unsubscriptions.rst:34
msgid ""
"The *Unsubscribe* link does **not** appear by default if the *Start From "
"Scratch* template is used to create a mailing. The user **must** manually "
"add the specific unsubscribe link `/unsubscribe_from_list` in the body of "
"the email, or use a block from the *Footers* section of the email builder, "
"which includes the unsubscribe link."
msgstr ""
"Tautan *Berhenti Berlangganan* **tidak** muncul secara default jika template "
"*Mulai Dari Awal* digunakan untuk membuat mailing. User **harus** "
"menambahkan tautan berhenti berlangganan spesifik `/unsubscribe_from_list` "
"secara manual di badan email, atau menggunakan blok dari bagian *Footer* "
"pembuat email, yang menyertakan tautan berhenti berlangganan."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/email_marketing/unsubscriptions.rst:39
msgid ""
"If a recipient clicks the *Unsubscribe* link in a mailing, Odoo instantly "
"unsubscribes them from the mailing list, presents them with "
"a :guilabel:`Mailing Subscriptions` page where they can directly manage "
"their subscriptions, and informs them that they've "
"been :guilabel:`Successfully Unsubscribed`."
msgstr ""
"Jika penerima mengklik tautan *Berhenti Berlangganan* dalam mailing, Odoo "
"langsung membatalkan langganan mereka dari daftar mailing, menampilkan "
"halaman :guilabel:`Langganan Mailing` di mana mereka dapat langsung "
"mengelola langganan mereka, dan memberi tahu mereka bahwa mereka telah "
":guilabel:`Berhasil Berhenti Berlangganan`."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/email_marketing/unsubscriptions.rst:None
msgid ""
"The Mailng Subscriptions page that appears when 'Unsubscribe' link in "
"mailing is clicked."
msgstr ""
"Halaman Langganan Mailing yang muncul ketika tautan 'Berhenti Berlangganan' "
"dalam mailing diklik."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/email_marketing/unsubscriptions.rst:48
msgid ""
"Beneath that, Odoo asks the former subscriber to :guilabel:`Please let us "
"know why you updated your subscription`, and the user can proceed to choose "
"the appropriate opt-out reason from a series of options presented to them."
msgstr ""
"Di bawahnya, Odoo meminta mantan pelanggan untuk :guilabel:`Mohon beri tahu "
"kami mengapa Anda memperbarui langganan Anda`, dan pengguna dapat "
"melanjutkan untuk memilih alasan opt-out yang sesuai dari serangkaian opsi "
"yang disajikan kepada mereka."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/email_marketing/unsubscriptions.rst:53
msgid ""
"The opt-out answer options can be created and modified by navigating "
"to :menuselection:`Email Marketing app --> Configuration --> Optout Reasons`."
msgstr ""
"Opsi jawaban opt-out dapat dibuat dan dimodifikasi dengan membuka "
":menuselection:`Aplikasi Email Marketing --> Konfigurasi --> Alasan Opt-out`."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/email_marketing/unsubscriptions.rst:56
msgid ""
"Once they've chosen the appropriate opt-out reason from the options "
"presented to them, they can click the :guilabel:`Send` button. Odoo then "
"logs their reasoning for unsubscribing in the *Email Marketing* app for "
"future analysis."
msgstr ""
"Setelah mereka memilih alasan opt-out yang sesuai dari opsi yang disajikan "
"kepada mereka, mereka dapat mengklik tombol :guilabel:`Kirim`. Odoo kemudian "
"mencatat alasan mereka untuk berhenti berlangganan di aplikasi *Email "
"Marketing* untuk analisis di masa mendatang."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/email_marketing/unsubscriptions.rst:61
#: ../../content/applications/marketing/sms_marketing/mailing_lists_blacklists.rst:102
msgid "Blacklist"
msgstr "Blacklist"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/email_marketing/unsubscriptions.rst:63
msgid ""
"For a recipient to remove (i.e. blacklist) themselves from **all** marketing "
"emails during the unsubscription process, on the :guilabel:`Mailing "
"Subscriptions` page, they must click :guilabel:`Exclude Me`."
msgstr ""
"Agar penerima dapat menghapus (yaitu memasukkan ke daftar hitam) diri mereka "
"sendiri dari **semua** email pemasaran selama proses berhenti berlangganan, "
"di halaman :guilabel:`Langganan Mailing`, mereka harus mengklik "
":guilabel:`Kecualikan Saya`."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/email_marketing/unsubscriptions.rst:67
msgid ""
"Upon clicking :guilabel:`Exclude Me`, Odoo informs the recipient they have "
"been successfully blacklisted, with a message reading: :guilabel:`✔️ Email "
"added to our blocklist`."
msgstr ""
"Setelah mengklik :guilabel:`Kecualikan Saya`, Odoo memberi tahu penerima "
"bahwa mereka telah berhasil masuk daftar hitam, dengan pesan yang berbunyi: "
":guilabel:`✔️ Email ditambahkan ke daftar blokir kami`."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/email_marketing/unsubscriptions.rst:None
msgid ""
"The blocklist question on the Mailing Subscriptions page that recipients see."
msgstr ""
"Pertanyaan daftar blokir di halaman Langganan Mailing yang dilihat penerima."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/email_marketing/unsubscriptions.rst:74
msgid ""
"Beneath that, Odoo asks the former subscriber to :guilabel:`Please let us "
"know why you want to be added to our blocklist`, and the user can proceed to "
"choose the appropriate reason from a series of options presented to them."
msgstr ""
"Di bawahnya, Odoo meminta mantan pelanggan untuk :guilabel:`Mohon beri tahu "
"kami mengapa Anda ingin ditambahkan ke daftar blokir kami`, dan pengguna "
"dapat melanjutkan untuk memilih alasan yang sesuai dari serangkaian opsi "
"yang disajikan kepada mereka."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/email_marketing/unsubscriptions.rst:78
msgid ""
"Once they've chosen the appropriate reason from the options presented to "
"them, they can click the :guilabel:`Send` button. Odoo then logs their "
"reasoning for blacklisting themselves in the *Email Marketing* app for "
"future analysis."
msgstr ""
"Setelah mereka memilih alasan yang sesuai dari opsi yang disajikan kepada "
"mereka, mereka dapat mengklik tombol :guilabel:`Kirim`. Odoo kemudian "
