"allowed to execute this rule. Leave the field empty to allow all groups. See "
"this documentation: :ref:`access-rights/groups`."
msgstr ""
"Di bawah tab :guilabel:`Actions To Do`, pilih :guilabel:`Add an action`. "
"Selanjutnya, di jendela pop-up :guilabel:`Create Actions` yang muncul, pilih "
":guilabel:`Send SMS`, dan atur :guilabel:`Allowed Groups`. "
":guilabel:`Allowed Groups` adalah grup hak akses yang diizinkan untuk "
"menjalankan aturan ini. Biarkan kolom kosong untuk mengizinkan semua grup. "
"Lihat dokumentasi ini: :ref:`access-rights/groups`."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/sms_marketing/sms_analysis.rst:84
msgid ""
