msgstr ""
"Tambahkan catatan yang diperlukan di bawah tab :guilabel:`Notes`. Terakhir, "
"navigasi keluar dari aturan otomasi yang telah selesai, atau simpan secara "
"manual (dengan mengklik ikon :guilabel:`☁️ (cloud)`), untuk menerapkan "
"perubahan."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/sms_marketing/twilio.rst:3
msgid "SMS via Twilio"
msgstr "SMS melalui Twilio"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/sms_marketing/twilio.rst:6
msgid "What is Twilio"
msgstr "Apa itu Twilio"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/sms_marketing/twilio.rst:8
msgid ""
"Twilio is a third-party provider that enables you to send SMS messages to "
"your clients. Odoo provides an easy way to use this service within your Odoo "
"apps."
msgstr ""
"Twilio adalah penyedia pihak ketiga yang memungkinkan Anda mengirim pesan "
"SMS ke klien Anda. Odoo menyediakan cara mudah untuk menggunakan layanan ini "
"di dalam aplikasi Odoo Anda."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/sms_marketing/twilio.rst:12
msgid "Why would I need it?"
msgstr "Mengapa saya memerlukannya?"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/sms_marketing/twilio.rst:14
msgid ""
"Although Odoo already comes with an out-of-the-box (IAP) solution for SMS "
"messages, it might not work in some countries with stricter legal "
"requirements. Currently, Odoo registers itself when possible to avoid extra "
"setup for its customers, however in some countries that is not enough and "
"the client itself must do it. This can be done through Twilio."
msgstr ""
"Meskipun Odoo sudah dilengkapi dengan solusi (IAP) siap pakai untuk pesan "
"SMS, solusi ini mungkin tidak berfungsi di beberapa negara dengan "
"persyaratan hukum yang lebih ketat. Saat ini, Odoo mendaftarkan dirinya "
"sendiri bila memungkinkan untuk menghindari pengaturan tambahan bagi "
"pelanggannya, namun di beberapa negara hal itu tidak cukup dan klien itu "
"sendiri harus melakukannya. Ini dapat dilakukan melalui Twilio."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/sms_marketing/twilio.rst:20
msgid "Setup your Twilio account"
msgstr "Siapkan akun Twilio Anda"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/sms_marketing/twilio.rst:22
msgid ""
"By creating a Twilio account, you will be able to create a virtual phone "
"number from which you will be able to send SMS messages. These cost credits "
"that are to be bought on Twilio, not Odoo."
msgstr ""
"Dengan membuat akun Twilio, Anda akan dapat membuat nomor telepon virtual "
"yang dapat Anda gunakan untuk mengirim pesan SMS. Biaya ini menggunakan "
"kredit yang harus dibeli di Twilio, bukan Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/sms_marketing/twilio.rst:25
msgid "Go to `Twilio <https://www.twilio.com>`_"
msgstr "Buka `Twilio <https://www.twilio.com>`_"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/sms_marketing/twilio.rst:26
msgid "Sign up and create a Twilio account"
msgstr "Daftar dan buat akun Twilio"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/sms_marketing/twilio.rst:27
msgid ""
"Within your Twilio account, you can create multiple accounts (e.g. one for "
"testing, one for each sub-company, etc.)"
msgstr ""
"Di dalam akun Twilio Anda, Anda dapat membuat beberapa akun (misalnya satu "
"untuk pengujian, satu untuk setiap sub-perusahaan, dll.)"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/sms_marketing/twilio.rst:29
msgid "Create a new account"
msgstr "Buat akun baru"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/sms_marketing/twilio.rst:31
msgid "Enter the name, and select :guilabel:`Twilio` for the type"
msgstr "Masukkan nama, dan pilih :guilabel:`Twilio` untuk jenisnya"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/sms_marketing/twilio.rst:32
msgid ""
"Select your :guilabel:`Billing Country` and click :guilabel:`Create new "
"account`"
msgstr ""
"Pilih :guilabel:`Billing Country` Anda dan klik :guilabel:`Create new "
"account`"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/sms_marketing/twilio.rst:33
msgid "Select the different options that match your needs"
msgstr "Pilih berbagai opsi yang sesuai dengan kebutuhan Anda"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/sms_marketing/twilio.rst:35
msgid "For the :guilabel:`Twilio product`, select :guilabel:`SMS`"
msgstr "Untuk :guilabel:`Twilio product`, pilih :guilabel:`SMS`"

