msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/sms_marketing/twilio.rst:67
msgid ""
"You can have multiple numbers (for instance once per country, or one per "
"campaign), in that case, you can reorder the numbers. By default, when "
"sending an SMS to a client, Odoo will select the number whose country is the "
"same as the client. If none matches, Odoo will use the first number "
"available from the list respecting the order you have chosen."
msgstr ""
"Anda dapat memiliki beberapa nomor (misalnya satu per negara, atau satu per "
"kampanye), dalam hal ini, Anda dapat menyusun ulang nomor tersebut. Secara "
"default, saat mengirim SMS ke klien, Odoo akan memilih nomor yang negaranya "
"sama dengan klien. Jika tidak ada yang cocok, Odoo akan menggunakan nomor "
"pertama yang tersedia dari daftar sesuai urutan yang telah Anda pilih."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/social_marketing.rst:5
msgid "Social Marketing"
msgstr "Marketing Sosial"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/social_marketing.rst:7
msgid ""
"Odoo's *Social Marketing* application helps content marketers create and "
"schedule posts, manage various social media accounts, analyze content "
"effectiveness, and engage directly with social media followers in one, "
"centralized location."
msgstr ""
"Aplikasi *Social Marketing* Odoo membantu pemasar konten membuat dan "
"menjadwalkan postingan, mengelola berbagai akun media sosial, menganalisis "
"efektivitas konten, dan berinteraksi langsung dengan pengikut media sosial "
"di satu lokasi terpusat."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/social_marketing.rst:16
#: ../../content/applications/marketing/social_marketing/social_posts.rst:3
msgid "Social posts"
msgstr "Postingan sosial"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/social_marketing.rst:16
msgid ""
"Discover everything there is to know about how to create and customize "
"social media posts using Odoo."
msgstr ""
"Temukan semua yang perlu diketahui tentang cara membuat dan menyesuaikan "
"postingan media sosial menggunakan Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/social_marketing.rst:22
msgid "Social campaigns"
msgstr "Kampanye sosial"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/social_marketing.rst:22
msgid ""
"Learn about all the different campaign and marketing tools this application "
"has to offer."
msgstr ""
"Pelajari semua alat kampanye dan marketing berbeda yang ditawarkan aplikasi "
"ini."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/social_marketing.rst:28
msgid "Social media accounts"
msgstr "Akun sosmed"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/social_marketing.rst:30
msgid ""
"In order to create social posts and analyze content with Odoo *Social "
"Marketing*, social media accounts **must** be added as a *stream* on the "
"application's main dashboard."
msgstr ""
"Untuk membuat postingan sosial dan menganalisis konten dengan Odoo *Social "
"Marketing*, akun media sosial **harus** ditambahkan sebagai *stream* di "
"dashboard utama aplikasi."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/social_marketing.rst:34
msgid ""
"Be aware that personal profiles **cannot** be added as a stream. The main "
"use of Odoo *Social Marketing* is to manage and analyze business accounts on "
"social media platforms."
msgstr ""
"Perlu diketahui bahwa profil pribadi **tidak dapat** ditambahkan sebagai "
"stream. Kegunaan utama Odoo *Social Marketing* adalah untuk mengelola dan "
"menganalisis akun bisnis di platform media sosial."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/social_marketing.rst:38
msgid ""
"Odoo *Social Marketing* has some limitations in regards to social media "
"accounts. For example, Odoo **cannot** handle a large quantity of various "
"pages (e.g. ~40 pages) under the same company. The same limitations are "
"present in a multi-company environment because of how the API is constructed."
msgstr ""
"Odoo *Social Marketing* memiliki beberapa keterbatasan terkait akun media "
"sosial. Misalnya, Odoo **tidak dapat** menangani sejumlah besar halaman yang "
"berbeda (misalnya ~40 halaman) di bawah perusahaan yang sama. Keterbatasan "
"yang sama juga ada di lingkungan multi-perusahaan karena cara API dibangun."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/social_marketing.rst:44
msgid ""
"In multi-company environments, if every company doesn't activate a page at "
"once, it will result in a permission error."
msgstr ""
"Di lingkungan multi-perusahaan, jika setiap perusahaan tidak mengaktifkan "
"halaman sekaligus, akan menghasilkan kesalahan izin."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/social_marketing.rst:47
msgid ""
"For example, if Company 1 is the only company selected from the main Odoo "
"dashboard, and activates *Facebook Page 1* and *Facebook Page 2*, then those "
"pages will be accesible on the *Social Marketing* dashboard."
msgstr ""
"Misalnya, jika Company 1 adalah satu-satunya perusahaan yang dipilih dari "
"dashboard Odoo utama, dan mengaktifkan *Facebook Page 1* dan *Facebook Page "
"2*, maka halaman-halaman tersebut akan dapat diakses di dashboard *Social "
"Marketing*."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/social_marketing.rst:51
msgid ""
"However, if on that same database, the user adds Company 2 from the company "
"drop-down menu in the header, and attempts to add those same streams, it "
"results in a permission error."
msgstr ""
"Namun, jika pada database yang sama, user menambahkan Company 2 dari menu "
"drop-down perusahaan di header, dan mencoba menambahkan stream yang sama, "
"akan menghasilkan kesalahan izin."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/social_marketing.rst:0
msgid ""
"View of the permission error that appears when incorrectly attempting to add "
"stream."
msgstr ""
"Tampilan kesalahan izin yang muncul saat salah mencoba menambahkan stream."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/social_marketing.rst:59
msgid "Social media streams"
msgstr "Stream media sosial"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/social_marketing.rst:61
msgid ""
"To add a social media business account as a stream, navigate "
"to :menuselection:`Social Marketing app` and select the :guilabel:`Add A "
"Stream` button located in the upper-left corner. Doing so reveals "
"an :guilabel:`Add a Stream` pop-up window."
msgstr ""
"Untuk menambahkan akun bisnis media sosial sebagai stream, buka "
":menuselection:`aplikasi Social Marketing` dan pilih tombol :guilabel:`Add A "
"Stream` yang terletak di pojok kiri atas. Hal ini akan memunculkan jendela "
"pop-up :guilabel:`Add a Stream`."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/social_marketing.rst:None
msgid ""
"View of the pop-up window that appears when Add a Stream is selected in Odoo."
msgstr "Tampilan jendela pop-up yang muncul saat Add a Stream dipilih di Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/social_marketing.rst:69
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Add a Stream` pop-up window, choose to :guilabel:`Link a "
"new account` for a business from any of the following popular social media "
"platforms: :guilabel:`Facebook`, :guilabel:`Instagram`, :guilabel:`LinkedIn`, :guilabel:`Twitter`, "
"and :guilabel:`YouTube`."
msgstr ""
"Di jendela pop-up :guilabel:`Add a Stream`, pilih untuk :guilabel:`Link a "
"new account` untuk bisnis dari salah satu platform media sosial populer "
"berikut: :guilabel:`Facebook`, :guilabel:`Instagram`, :guilabel:`LinkedIn`, "
":guilabel:`Twitter`, dan :guilabel:`YouTube`."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/social_marketing.rst:73
msgid ""
"After clicking the desired social media outlet from the :guilabel:`Add a "
"Stream` pop-up window, Odoo navigates directly to that specific social media "
"outlet's authorization page, where permission must be granted, in order for "
"Odoo to add that particular social media account as a stream to the *Social "
"Marketing* application."
msgstr ""
"Setelah mengklik platform media sosial yang diinginkan dari jendela pop-up "
":guilabel:`Add a Stream`, Odoo akan menavigasi langsung ke halaman otorisasi "
"platform media sosial tersebut, di mana izin harus diberikan agar Odoo dapat "
"menambahkan akun media sosial tersebut sebagai stream ke aplikasi *Social "
"Marketing*."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/social_marketing.rst:None
msgid ""
"Sample of a populated social marketing dashboard with social media streams "
"and content."
msgstr ""
"Contoh dashboard Social Marketing yang terisi dengan stream media sosial dan "
"konten."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/social_marketing.rst:82
msgid ""
"Once permission is granted, Odoo navigates back to the :guilabel:`Feed` on "
"the main :guilabel:`Social Marketing` dashboard, and a new column, with that "
"account's posts, is added. Accounts/streams can be added at any time."
msgstr ""
"Setelah izin diberikan, Odoo akan kembali ke :guilabel:`Feed` di dashboard "
":guilabel:`Social Marketing` utama, dan kolom baru dengan postingan akun "
"tersebut akan ditambahkan. Akun/stream dapat ditambahkan kapan saja."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/social_marketing.rst:87
msgid ""
"A :guilabel:`Facebook` page can be added as long as the :guilabel:`Facebook` "
"account that grants permission is the administrator for the page. It should "
"also be noted that different pages can be added for different streams."
msgstr ""
"Halaman :guilabel:`Facebook` dapat ditambahkan selama akun "
":guilabel:`Facebook` yang memberikan izin adalah administrator untuk halaman "
"tersebut. Perlu juga dicatat bahwa halaman yang berbeda dapat ditambahkan "
"untuk stream yang berbeda."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/social_marketing.rst:92
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Instagram` accounts are added through a :guilabel:`Facebook` "
"login because it uses the same API. This means, an :guilabel:`Instagram` "
"account needs to be linked to a :guilabel:`Facebook` account in order for it "
"to show up as a stream in Odoo."
msgstr ""
"Akun :guilabel:`Instagram` ditambahkan melalui login :guilabel:`Facebook` "
"karena menggunakan API yang sama. Ini berarti, akun :guilabel:`Instagram` "
"perlu ditautkan ke akun :guilabel:`Facebook` agar dapat muncul sebagai "
"stream di Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/social_marketing.rst:97
msgid "Social media page"
msgstr "Halaman media sosial"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/social_marketing.rst:99
msgid ""
"Another way to quickly link social media accounts to Odoo *Social Marketing* "
"can be done on the :guilabel:`Social Media` page. To access "
"the :guilabel:`Social Media` page, navigate to :menuselection:`Social "
"Marketing app --> Configuration --> Social Media`."
msgstr ""
"Cara lain untuk menautkan akun media sosial ke Odoo *Social Marketing* "
"dengan cepat dapat dilakukan di halaman :guilabel:`Social Media`. Untuk "
"mengakses halaman :guilabel:`Social Media`, buka :menuselection:`aplikasi "
"Social Marketing --> Configuration --> Social Media`."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/social_marketing.rst:103
msgid ""
"On the :guilabel:`Social Media` page there is a collection of all social "
"media options, each complete with a :guilabel:`Link account` "
"button: :guilabel:`Facebook`, :guilabel:`Instagram`, :guilabel:`LinkedIn`, :guilabel:`Twitter`, :guilabel:`YouTube`, "
"and :guilabel:`Push Notifications`."
msgstr ""
"Di halaman :guilabel:`Social Media` terdapat kumpulan semua opsi media "
"sosial, masing-masing dilengkapi dengan tombol :guilabel:`Link account`: "
":guilabel:`Facebook`, :guilabel:`Instagram`, :guilabel:`LinkedIn`, "
":guilabel:`Twitter`, :guilabel:`YouTube`, dan :guilabel:`Push Notifications`."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/social_marketing.rst:None
msgid "View of the social media page in the Odoo Social Marketing application."
msgstr "Tampilan halaman Social Media di aplikasi Odoo Social Marketing."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/social_marketing.rst:112
msgid "Social accounts page"
msgstr "Halaman akun sosial"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/social_marketing.rst:114
msgid ""
"To see a list of all social accounts and websites linked to the database, go "
"to :menuselection:`Social Marketing app --> Configuration --> Social "
"Accounts`. This :guilabel:`Social Accounts` display the :guilabel:`Name`, "
"the :guilabel:`Handle/Short Name`, the :guilabel:`Social Media` platform, "
"who it was :guilabel:`Created by`, and the :guilabel:`Company` to which it "
"is associated."
msgstr ""
"Untuk melihat daftar semua akun sosial dan situs web yang terhubung ke "
"database, buka :menuselection:`Aplikasi Social Marketing --> Konfigurasi --> "
"Akun Sosial`. :guilabel:`Akun Sosial` ini menampilkan :guilabel:`Nama`, "
":guilabel:`Handle/Nama Pendek`, platform :guilabel:`Media Sosial`, "
":guilabel:`Dibuat oleh` siapa, dan :guilabel:`Perusahaan` yang terkait "
"dengannya."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/social_marketing.rst:None
msgid ""
"View of the social accounts page in the Odoo Social Marketing application."
msgstr "Tampilan halaman akun sosial di aplikasi Odoo Social Marketing."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/social_marketing.rst:124
msgid ""
"To edit/modify any of the social accounts on this page, simply select the "
"desired account from the list on this page, and proceed to make any "
"adjustments necessary."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mengedit/mengubah salah satu akun sosial di halaman ini, cukup pilih "
"akun yang diinginkan dari daftar di halaman ini, dan lanjutkan untuk "
"melakukan penyesuaian yang diperlukan."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/social_marketing.rst:128
msgid "Social streams page"
msgstr "Halaman streaming sosial"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/social_marketing.rst:130
msgid ""
"To view a separate page with all the social media streams that have been "
"added to the main *Social Marketing* dashboard, navigate "
"to :menuselection:`Social Marketing app --> Configuration --> Social "
"Streams`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk melihat halaman terpisah dengan semua streaming media sosial yang "
"telah ditambahkan ke dashboard *Social Marketing* utama, navigasikan ke "
":menuselection:`Aplikasi Social Marketing --> Konfigurasi --> Streaming "
"Sosial`."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/social_marketing.rst:138
msgid ""
"Here, the social stream information is organized in a list with "
"the :guilabel:`Social Media`, the :guilabel:`Title` of the stream, "
"the :guilabel:`Type` of the stream "
"(e.g. :guilabel:`Posts`, :guilabel:`Keyword`, etc.), who it "
"was :guilabel:`Created by`, and  the :guilabel:`Company` to which it is "
"associated."
msgstr ""
"Di sini, informasi streaming sosial diatur dalam daftar dengan "
":guilabel:`Media Sosial`, :guilabel:`Judul` streaming, :guilabel:`Tipe` "
"streaming (misalnya :guilabel:`Postingan`, :guilabel:`Kata Kunci`, dll.), "
":guilabel:`Dibuat oleh` siapa, dan :guilabel:`Perusahaan` yang terkait "
"dengannya."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/social_marketing.rst:143
msgid ""
"To modify any stream's information, simply click the desired stream from the "
"list, and proceed to make any necessary adjustments."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mengubah informasi streaming apa pun, cukup klik streaming yang "
"diinginkan dari daftar, dan lanjutkan untuk melakukan penyesuaian yang "
"diperlukan."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/social_marketing.rst:147
msgid "Visitors"
msgstr "Pengunjung"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/social_marketing.rst:149
msgid ""
"To see a complete overview of all the people who have visited the website(s) "
"connected to the database, navigate to :menuselection:`Social Marketing app "
"--> Visitors`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk melihat gambaran lengkap semua orang yang telah mengunjungi situs web "
"yang terhubung ke database, navigasikan ke :menuselection:`Aplikasi Social "
"Marketing --> Pengunjung`."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/social_marketing.rst:None
msgid "View of the Visitors page in the Odoo Social Marketing application."
msgstr "Tampilan halaman Pengunjung di aplikasi Odoo Social Marketing."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/social_marketing.rst:156
msgid ""
"Here, Odoo provides a detailed layout of all the visitors' pertinent "
"information in a default kanban view. If visitors already have contact "
"information in the database, the option to send them an :guilabel:`Email` "
"and/or an :guilabel:`SMS` is available."
msgstr ""
"Di sini, Odoo menyediakan tata letak terperinci dari semua informasi penting "
"pengunjung dalam tampilan kanban default. Jika pengunjung sudah memiliki "
"informasi kontak di database, opsi untuk mengirim :guilabel:`Email` dan/atau "
":guilabel:`SMS` kepada mereka tersedia."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/social_marketing.rst:160
msgid ""
"This same visitor data can also be viewed as a list or a graph. Those view "
"options are located in the upper-right corner of the :guilabel:`Visitors` "
"page."
msgstr ""
"Data pengunjung yang sama ini juga dapat dilihat sebagai daftar atau grafik. "
"Opsi tampilan tersebut terletak di pojok kanan atas halaman "
":guilabel:`Pengunjung`."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/social_marketing/social_campaigns.rst:3
msgid "Social marketing campaigns"
msgstr "Kampanye pemasaran sosial"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/social_marketing/social_campaigns.rst:5
msgid ""
"Social marketing campaigns help companies connect directly with the "
"marketplace. These campaigns are helpful when introducing a new product to "
"customers, explaining the value of a product or service, or when advertising "
"an upcoming event or product release."
msgstr ""
"Kampanye pemasaran sosial membantu perusahaan terhubung langsung dengan "
"pasar. Kampanye ini berguna ketika memperkenalkan produk baru kepada "
"pelanggan, menjelaskan nilai produk atau layanan, atau ketika mengiklankan "
"acara atau peluncuran produk yang akan datang."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/social_marketing/social_campaigns.rst:9
msgid ""
"The most effective social marketing campaigns typically involve multiple "
"channels to maximize content distribution, and Odoo's *Social Marketing* "
"application acts as a singular control center to monitor, plan, post, track, "
"and analyze all of the various content and content channels within a single "
"dashboard."
msgstr ""
"Kampanye pemasaran sosial yang paling efektif biasanya melibatkan beberapa "
"saluran untuk memaksimalkan distribusi konten, dan aplikasi *Social "
"Marketing* Odoo bertindak sebagai pusat kontrol tunggal untuk memantau, "
"merencanakan, memposting, melacak, dan menganalisis semua konten dan saluran "
"konten yang berbeda dalam satu dashboard."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/social_marketing/social_campaigns.rst:17
msgid ""
"To access a complete overview of all social marketing campaigns, open "
"the :menuselection:`Social Marketing` application, and "
"click :menuselection:`Campaigns` from the header menu. Doing so reveals a "
"separate page with every campaign in a default kanban view."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mengakses gambaran lengkap semua kampanye pemasaran sosial, buka "
"aplikasi :menuselection:`Social Marketing`, dan klik "
":menuselection:`Kampanye` dari menu header. Melakukan hal ini akan "
"menampilkan halaman terpisah dengan setiap kampanye dalam tampilan kanban "
"default."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/social_marketing/social_campaigns.rst:None
msgid "View of the campaigns page in the Odoo Social Marketing application."
msgstr "Tampilan halaman kampanye di aplikasi Odoo Social Marketing."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/social_marketing/social_campaigns.rst:25
msgid ""
"Each *stage* in the kanban view can be edited, by clicking "
"the :guilabel:`gear icon` to the left of the :guilabel:`+ (plus sign)` - "
"located to the right of the stage title."
msgstr ""
"Setiap *tahap* dalam tampilan kanban dapat diedit, dengan mengklik "
":guilabel:`ikon roda gigi` di sebelah kiri :guilabel:`+ (tanda plus)` - yang "
"terletak di sebelah kanan judul tahap."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/social_marketing/social_campaigns.rst:29
msgid ""
"The **gear icon** *only* appears when the cursor hovers to the left of the "
"**+ (plus sign)**. When the gear icon is clicked, a drop-down menu reveals "
"the options: :guilabel:`Fold`, :guilabel:`Edit Stage`, "
"and :guilabel:`Delete`."
msgstr ""
"**Ikon roda gigi** *hanya* muncul ketika kursor melayang di sebelah kiri **+ "
"(tanda plus)**. Ketika ikon roda gigi diklik, menu drop-down menampilkan "
"opsi: :guilabel:`Lipat`, :guilabel:`Edit Tahap`, dan :guilabel:`Hapus`."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/social_marketing/social_campaigns.rst:37
msgid ""
"Clicking :guilabel:`Fold` minimizes that specific stage's column. The stage "
"column can be restored by clicking the folded version of it on the "
"main :guilabel:`Campaigns` dashboard in the default kanban view."
msgstr ""
"Mengklik :guilabel:`Lipat` meminimalkan kolom tahap tertentu tersebut. Kolom "
"tahap dapat dipulihkan dengan mengklik versi terlipat di dashboard "
":guilabel:`Kampanye` utama dalam tampilan kanban default."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/social_marketing/social_campaigns.rst:41
msgid ""
"Selecting :guilabel:`Edit Stage` reveals a pop-up window, in which the name "
"and the sequence of the stage can be modified. If changes are made, be sure "
"to click :guilabel:`Save`."
msgstr ""
"Memilih :guilabel:`Edit Stage` menampilkan jendela pop-up, di mana nama dan "
"urutan tahap dapat diubah. Jika ada perubahan, pastikan untuk mengklik "
":guilabel:`Save`."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/social_marketing/social_campaigns.rst:44
msgid "Clicking :guilabel:`Delete` removes the stage entirely."
msgstr "Mengklik :guilabel:`Delete` menghapus tahap sepenuhnya."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/social_marketing/social_campaigns.rst:47
msgid ""
"To add a new stage to the pipeline, side-scroll to the right on "
"the :guilabel:`Campaigns` dashboard, click :guilabel:`Add a Column`, enter "
"in the desired information, and click :guilabel:`Add`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk menambahkan tahap baru ke pipeline, gulir ke kanan pada dashboard "
":guilabel:`Campaigns`, klik :guilabel:`Add a Column`, masukkan informasi "
"yang diinginkan, dan klik :guilabel:`Add`."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/social_marketing/social_campaigns.rst:52
msgid ""
"The same social marketing campaign information on the :guilabel:`Campaigns` "
"dashboard can also be viewed as a list, by selecting the :guilabel:`List` "
"option, located under the search bar, in the upper-right corner."
msgstr ""
"Informasi kampanye social marketing yang sama pada dashboard "
":guilabel:`Campaigns` juga dapat dilihat sebagai daftar, dengan memilih opsi "
":guilabel:`List`, yang terletak di bawah bilah pencarian, di sudut kanan "
"atas."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/social_marketing/social_campaigns.rst:57
msgid "Create social marketing campaigns"
msgstr "Membuat kampanye social marketing"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/social_marketing/social_campaigns.rst:59
msgid ""
"First, open the :menuselection:`Social Marketing` application, and "
"select :guilabel:`Campaigns` from the header menu."
msgstr ""
"Pertama, buka aplikasi :menuselection:`Social Marketing`, dan pilih "
":guilabel:`Campaigns` dari menu header."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/social_marketing/social_campaigns.rst:62
msgid ""
"On the :guilabel:`Campaigns` dashboard, a new campaign can be created by "
"clicking the quick add :guilabel:`+ (plus sign)` located in the top-right "
"corner of each stage in the pipeline, visible in the kanban view. Campaigns "
"can also be created by clicking :guilabel:`Create` in the upper-left corner "
"of the :guilabel:`Campaigns` dashboard."
msgstr ""
"Pada dashboard :guilabel:`Campaigns`, kampanye baru dapat dibuat dengan "
"mengklik tombol tambah cepat :guilabel:`+ (plus sign)` yang terletak di "
"sudut kanan atas setiap tahap dalam pipeline, terlihat dalam tampilan "
"kanban. Kampanye juga dapat dibuat dengan mengklik :guilabel:`Create` di "
"sudut kiri atas dashboard :guilabel:`Campaigns`."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/social_marketing/social_campaigns.rst:67
msgid ""
"Both options reveal a new campaign detail window directly on "
"the :guilabel:`Campaigns` dashboard when clicked."
msgstr ""
"Kedua opsi menampilkan jendela detail kampanye baru langsung pada dashboard "
":guilabel:`Campaigns` saat diklik."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/social_marketing/social_campaigns.rst:None
msgid "View of the quick add option for campaigns in Odoo Social Marketing."
msgstr "Tampilan opsi tambah cepat untuk kampanye di Odoo Social Marketing."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/social_marketing/social_campaigns.rst:74
msgid ""
"Here, the :guilabel:`Campaign Name`, :guilabel:`Responsible`, "
"and :guilabel:`Tags` can be entered. When all modifications are complete, "
"click :guilabel:`Add` to add the campaign to the database."
msgstr ""
"Di sini, :guilabel:`Campaign Name`, :guilabel:`Responsible`, dan "
":guilabel:`Tags` dapat dimasukkan. Setelah semua modifikasi selesai, klik "
":guilabel:`Add` untuk menambahkan kampanye ke database."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/social_marketing/social_campaigns.rst:78
msgid "Edit social marketing campaigns"
msgstr "Mengedit kampanye social marketing"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/social_marketing/social_campaigns.rst:80
msgid ""
"In order to edit a campaign in greater detail, and create/send various forms "
"of communications related to it, the template page for that campaign must be "
"accessed and modified, accordingly. There are multiple ways to access a "
"template page for a campaign."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mengedit kampanye secara lebih detail, dan membuat/mengirim berbagai "
"bentuk komunikasi yang terkait dengannya, halaman template untuk kampanye "
"tersebut harus diakses dan dimodifikasi sesuai kebutuhan. Ada beberapa cara "
"untuk mengakses halaman template untuk kampanye."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/social_marketing/social_campaigns.rst:84
msgid ""
"After entering the pertinent information in the :guilabel:`Quick Add` "
"campaign drop-down, click :guilabel:`Edit`."
msgstr ""
"Setelah memasukkan informasi yang relevan dalam drop-down kampanye "
":guilabel:`Quick Add`, klik :guilabel:`Edit`."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/social_marketing/social_campaigns.rst:86
msgid ""
"Simply select the desired campaign from the :guilabel:`Campaigns` dashboard "
"in list or kanban view."
msgstr ""
"Cukup pilih kampanye yang diinginkan dari dashboard :guilabel:`Campaigns` "
"dalam tampilan daftar atau kanban."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/social_marketing/social_campaigns.rst:88
msgid ""
"On the :guilabel:`Campaigns` dashboard in the kanban view, select "
"the :guilabel:`⋮ (three dots)` drop-down menu on the desired campaign, and "
"select :guilabel:`Edit`."
msgstr ""
"Pada dashboard :guilabel:`Campaigns` dalam tampilan kanban, pilih menu drop-"
"down :guilabel:`⋮ (three dots)` pada kampanye yang diinginkan, dan pilih "
":guilabel:`Edit`."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/social_marketing/social_campaigns.rst:91
msgid ""
"Any of the above routes will reveal the *Campaign Template* page for that "
"specific campaign."
msgstr ""
"Salah satu rute di atas akan menampilkan halaman *Campaign Template* untuk "
"kampanye spesifik tersebut."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/social_marketing/social_campaigns.rst:94
msgid "Social marketing campaign templates"
msgstr "Template kampanye social marketing"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/social_marketing/social_campaigns.rst:96
msgid ""
"On a *Campaign Template* page, numerous elements can be customized/modified, "
"and various forms of communications can be created, modified, and sent or "
"scheduled. Below is a sample of a completed campaign template."
msgstr ""
"Pada halaman *Campaign Template*, berbagai elemen dapat disesuaikan/"
"dimodifikasi, dan berbagai bentuk komunikasi dapat dibuat, dimodifikasi, dan "
"dikirim atau dijadwalkan. Berikut adalah contoh template kampanye yang sudah "
"selesai."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/social_marketing/social_campaigns.rst:None
msgid "View of a sample campaign template page in Odoo Social Marketing."
msgstr "Tampilan contoh halaman template kampanye di Odoo Social Marketing."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/social_marketing/social_campaigns.rst:105
msgid ""
"In order for the :guilabel:`Send New Mailing` option to appear on campaign "
"templates, make sure the *Mailing Campaigns* feature is enabled in the "
"*Email Marketing* app. To do that, navigate to :menuselection:`Email "
"Marketing --> Configuration --> Settings`, activate :guilabel:`Mailing "
"Campaigns`, and click :guilabel:`Save`."
msgstr ""
"Agar opsi :guilabel:`Send New Mailing` muncul pada template kampanye, "
"pastikan fitur *Mailing Campaigns* diaktifkan di aplikasi *Email Marketing*. "
"Untuk melakukannya, navigasikan ke :menuselection:`Email Marketing --> "
"Configuration --> Settings`, aktifkan :guilabel:`Mailing Campaigns`, dan "
"klik :guilabel:`Save`."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/social_marketing/social_campaigns.rst:111
msgid ""
"In order for the :guilabel:`Send SMS` option to appear, the Odoo *SMS "
"Marketing* application must be installed on the database."
msgstr ""
"Agar opsi :guilabel:`Send SMS` muncul, aplikasi Odoo *SMS Marketing* harus "
"diinstal pada database."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/social_marketing/social_campaigns.rst:115
msgid "Add content and communications to campaigns"
msgstr "Tambahkan konten dan komunikasi ke kampanye"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/social_marketing/social_campaigns.rst:117
msgid ""
"If the proper settings and applications are installed (as instructed above), "
"there are four forms of communication/content options that can be added to "
"campaigns. Each of these options are displayed as buttons in the upper-left "
"corner of the campaign template page."
msgstr ""
"Jika pengaturan yang tepat dan aplikasi telah diinstal (seperti yang "
"diinstruksikan di atas), ada empat bentuk opsi komunikasi/konten yang dapat "
"ditambahkan ke kampanye. Setiap opsi ini ditampilkan sebagai tombol di sudut "
"kiri atas halaman template kampanye."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/social_marketing/social_campaigns.rst:121
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Send New Mailing`: reveals a blank email template on a separate "
"page, in which the message can be fully customized in a variety of ways."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Send New Mailing`: menampilkan template email kosong pada halaman "
"terpisah, di mana pesan dapat disesuaikan sepenuhnya dalam berbagai cara."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/social_marketing/social_campaigns.rst:123
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Send SMS`: reveals a blank SMS template on a separate page, in "
"which a SMS communication can be created and configured."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Send SMS`: menampilkan template SMS kosong pada halaman terpisah, "
"di mana komunikasi SMS dapat dibuat dan dikonfigurasi."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/social_marketing/social_campaigns.rst:125
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Send Social Post`: reveals a blank social post template on a "
"separate page, in which a post can be created, and applied to social media "
"accounts that are already connected to the database."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Send Social Post`: menampilkan template postingan sosial kosong "
"pada halaman terpisah, di mana postingan dapat dibuat dan diterapkan ke akun "
"media sosial yang sudah terhubung ke database."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/social_marketing/social_campaigns.rst:128
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Push Notification`: reveals a similar blank social post template "
"on a separate page, however, the :guilabel:`Push Notification` options are "
"already pre-selected in the :guilabel:`Post on` field."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Push Notification`: menampilkan template postingan sosial kosong "
"yang serupa pada halaman terpisah, namun, opsi :guilabel:`Push Notification` "
"sudah dipilih sebelumnya di bidang :guilabel:`Post on`."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/social_marketing/social_campaigns.rst:132
msgid ""
"Whichever form of communication is created, once it's completed, Odoo "
"returns to the :guilabel:`Campaign Template` page, showcasing that new "
"content in its corresponding tab "
"(e.g. :guilabel:`Mailings`, :guilabel:`SMS`, :guilabel:`Social Media`, and/"
"or :guilabel:`Push Notifications`)."
msgstr ""
"Bentuk komunikasi apa pun yang dibuat, setelah selesai, Odoo kembali ke "
"halaman :guilabel:`Campaign Template`, menampilkan konten baru tersebut di "
"tab yang sesuai (misalnya :guilabel:`Mailings`, :guilabel:`SMS`, "
":guilabel:`Social Media`, dan/atau :guilabel:`Push Notifications`)."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/social_marketing/social_campaigns.rst:137
msgid ""
"As content and communications are added to a campaign, tabs for those "
"specific mediums appear, along with a variety of analytical smart buttons "
"(e.g. :guilabel:`Revenues`, :guilabel:`Quotations`, :guilabel:`Leads`, etc.)."
msgstr ""
"Saat konten dan komunikasi ditambahkan ke kampanye, tab untuk media spesifik "
"tersebut muncul, bersama dengan berbagai tombol pintar analitik (misalnya "
":guilabel:`Revenues`, :guilabel:`Quotations`, :guilabel:`Leads`, dll.)."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/social_marketing/social_campaigns.rst:141
msgid ""
"These smart buttons, located at the top of the template, display different "
"metrics related to the campaign, and its various communications and content. "
"Clicking any smart button reveals a separate page dedicated to that "
"particular element of the campaign, allowing for quicker, more organized "
"analysis."
msgstr ""
"Tombol pintar ini, yang terletak di bagian atas template, menampilkan metrik "
"berbeda yang terkait dengan kampanye dan berbagai komunikasi serta "
"kontennya. Mengklik tombol pintar apa pun menampilkan halaman terpisah yang "
"didedikasikan untuk elemen tertentu dari kampanye, memungkinkan analisis "
"yang lebih cepat dan lebih terorganisir."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/social_marketing/social_campaigns.rst:147
msgid ""
"The Odoo *Social Marketing* app is integrated with other Odoo applications, "
"such as *Sales*, *Invoicing*, *CRM*, and *Website*."
msgstr ""
"Aplikasi Odoo *Social Marketing* terintegrasi dengan aplikasi Odoo lainnya, "
"seperti *Penjualan*, *Penagihan*, *CRM*, dan *Website*."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/social_marketing/social_posts.rst:5
msgid ""
"The Odoo *Social Marketing* application provides various ways to create "
"posts for any type of social media outlet."
msgstr ""
"Aplikasi Odoo *Social Marketing* menyediakan berbagai cara untuk membuat "
"postingan untuk semua jenis outlet media sosial."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/social_marketing/social_posts.rst:9
msgid "Posts page"
msgstr "Halaman postingan"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/social_marketing/social_posts.rst:11
msgid ""
"To see a complete overview of posts, go to Odoo :menuselection:`Social "
"Marketing app --> Posts`. Here, on the :guilabel:`Social Posts` page, every "
"post that has been created and posted with Odoo can be seen and accessed."
msgstr ""
"Untuk melihat gambaran lengkap postingan, buka :menuselection:`aplikasi "
"Social Marketing Odoo --> Posts`. Di sini, pada halaman :guilabel:`Social "
"Posts`, setiap postingan yang telah dibuat dan diposting dengan Odoo dapat "
"dilihat dan diakses."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/social_marketing/social_posts.rst:15
msgid ""
"There are four different view options for the :guilabel:`Social Posts` page "
"data: *kanban*, *calendar*, *list*, and *pivot*."
msgstr ""
"Ada empat opsi tampilan berbeda untuk data halaman :guilabel:`Social Posts`: "
"*kanban*, *kalender*, *daftar*, dan *pivot*."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/social_marketing/social_posts.rst:18
msgid ""
"The view options are located in the upper right corner of "
"the :guilabel:`Posts` page, beneath the search bar."
msgstr ""
"Opsi tampilan terletak di sudut kanan atas halaman :guilabel:`Posts`, di "
"bawah bilah pencarian."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/social_marketing/social_posts.rst:25
msgid ""
"By default, Odoo displays the posts in a kanban view. The information on "
"this page can be sorted even further, via the left sidebar, where all "
"connected social accounts and posts can be quickly seen, accessed, and "
"analyzed."
msgstr ""
"Secara default, Odoo menampilkan postingan dalam tampilan kanban. Informasi "
"pada halaman ini dapat diurutkan lebih lanjut melalui sidebar kiri, di mana "
"semua akun sosial dan postingan yang terhubung dapat dengan cepat dilihat, "
"diakses, dan dianalisis."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/social_marketing/social_posts.rst:29
msgid ""
"The kanban view is represented by an :guilabel:`inverted bar graph icon` in "
"the upper-right corner."
msgstr ""
"Tampilan kanban diwakili oleh :guilabel:`ikon grafik batang terbalik` di "
"sudut kanan atas."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/social_marketing/social_posts.rst:0
msgid "Kanban view of the posts page in the Odoo Social Marketing application."
msgstr ""
"Tampilan kanban dari halaman postingan di aplikasi Social Marketing Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/social_marketing/social_posts.rst:38
msgid ""
"The calendar view option displays a visual representation of posts in a "
"calendar format of when posts were published, or are scheduled to be "
"published. This option provides a clear overview of any planned day, week, "
"or month, and Odoo displays all drafted, scheduled, and published posts."
msgstr ""
"Opsi tampilan kalender menampilkan representasi visual dari postingan dalam "
"format kalender tentang kapan postingan dipublikasikan atau dijadwalkan "
"untuk dipublikasikan. Opsi ini memberikan gambaran yang jelas tentang hari, "
"minggu, atau bulan yang direncanakan, dan Odoo menampilkan semua postingan "
"yang didraf, dijadwalkan, dan dipublikasikan."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/social_marketing/social_posts.rst:43
msgid ""
"Clicking on a date reveals a blank social media post detail form, in which a "
"social media post can be created, and Odoo will post it on that specific "
"date/time."
msgstr ""
"Mengklik tanggal akan menampilkan formulir detail postingan media sosial "
"kosong, di mana postingan media sosial dapat dibuat, dan Odoo akan "
"mempostingnya pada tanggal/waktu tertentu tersebut."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/social_marketing/social_posts.rst:46
msgid ""
"The calendar view is represented by a :guilabel:`calendar icon` in the upper-"
"right corner."
msgstr ""
"Tampilan kalender direpresentasikan oleh :guilabel:`ikon kalender` di sudut "
"kanan atas."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/social_marketing/social_posts.rst:0
msgid "Example of the calendar view in Odoo Social Marketing."
msgstr "Contoh tampilan kalender di Odoo Social Marketing."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/social_marketing/social_posts.rst:54
msgid ""
"The list view option is similar to the kanban option, but instead of "
"individual blocks, all post information is displayed in a clear, list "
"layout. Each line of the list displays the :guilabel:`Social "
"Accounts`, :guilabel:`Message`, and :guilabel:`Status` of every post."
msgstr ""
"Opsi tampilan daftar mirip dengan opsi kanban, tetapi alih-alih blok "
"individual, semua informasi postingan ditampilkan dalam tata letak daftar "
"yang jelas. Setiap baris daftar menampilkan :guilabel:`Akun Sosial`, "
":guilabel:`Pesan`, dan :guilabel:`Status` dari setiap postingan."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/social_marketing/social_posts.rst:58
msgid ""
"There is also a helpful left sidebar that organizes all posts "
"by :guilabel:`Status` and lists all connected :guilabel:`Social Accounts`, "
"as well."
msgstr ""
"Ada juga sidebar kiri yang membantu yang mengorganisir semua postingan "
"berdasarkan :guilabel:`Status` dan mencantumkan semua :guilabel:`Akun "
"Sosial` yang terhubung juga."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/social_marketing/social_posts.rst:61
msgid ""
"The list view is represented by four vertical lines in the upper-right "
"corner."
msgstr ""
"Tampilan daftar direpresentasikan oleh empat garis vertikal di sudut kanan "
"atas."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/social_marketing/social_posts.rst:0
msgid "View of the list option on the posts page in Odoo Social Marketing."
msgstr "Tampilan opsi daftar pada halaman postingan di Odoo Social Marketing."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/social_marketing/social_posts.rst:67
msgid "Pivot view"
msgstr "Tampilan pivot"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/social_marketing/social_posts.rst:69
msgid ""
"The pivot view option provides a fully customizable grid table, where "
"different measures of data can be added and analyzed."
msgstr ""
"Opsi tampilan pivot menyediakan tabel grid yang sepenuhnya dapat "
"disesuaikan, di mana berbagai ukuran data dapat ditambahkan dan dianalisis."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/social_marketing/social_posts.rst:0
msgid "View of the pivot option on the posts page in Odoo Social Marketing."
msgstr "Tampilan opsi pivot pada halaman postingan di Odoo Social Marketing."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/social_marketing/social_posts.rst:76
msgid ""
"The pivot view option provides numerous analytical options, allowing for in-"
"depth, detailed analysis of various posts and metrics."
msgstr ""
"Opsi tampilan pivot menyediakan berbagai opsi analitis, memungkinkan "
"analisis mendalam dan terperinci dari berbagai postingan dan metrik."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/social_marketing/social_posts.rst:79
msgid ""
"Click on any :guilabel:`➕ (plus sign) icon` next to a line in the pivot "
"table to reveal more metric options to add to the grid."
msgstr ""
"Klik ikon :guilabel:`➕ (tanda plus)` di samping baris dalam tabel pivot "
"untuk menampilkan lebih banyak opsi metrik yang dapat ditambahkan ke grid."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/social_marketing/social_posts.rst:82
msgid ""
"While in the pivot view, the option to :guilabel:`Insert in Spreadsheet` is "
"available, located to the right of the :guilabel:`Measures` drop-down menu, "
"in the upper-left corner of the :guilabel:`Social Posts` page."
msgstr ""
"Saat berada di tampilan pivot, opsi untuk :guilabel:`Sisipkan di "
"Spreadsheet` tersedia, terletak di sebelah kanan menu drop-down "
":guilabel:`Ukuran`, di sudut kiri atas halaman :guilabel:`Postingan Sosial`."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/social_marketing/social_posts.rst:86
msgid ""
"Next to the :guilabel:`Insert in Spreadsheet` are three options, specific to "
"the pivot view."
msgstr ""
"Di samping :guilabel:`Sisipkan di Spreadsheet` terdapat tiga opsi, khusus "
"untuk tampilan pivot."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/social_marketing/social_posts.rst:88
msgid "From left to right, those options are:"
msgstr "Dari kiri ke kanan, opsi tersebut adalah:"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/social_marketing/social_posts.rst:90
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Flip Axis`, which switches the *X* and *Y* axis in the grid table."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Balik Sumbu`, yang menukar sumbu *X* dan *Y* di tabel grid."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/social_marketing/social_posts.rst:91
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Expand All`, which expands each line in the grid, revealing more "
"detailed information related to it."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Perluas Semua`, yang memperluas setiap baris di grid, menampilkan "
"informasi lebih terperinci yang terkait dengannya."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/social_marketing/social_posts.rst:93
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Download`, which, when clicked, instantly downloads the pivot "
"table as a spreadsheet."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Unduh`, yang ketika diklik, langsung mengunduh tabel pivot "
"sebagai spreadsheet."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/social_marketing/social_posts.rst:97
msgid "Posts"
msgstr "kiriman"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/social_marketing/social_posts.rst:99
msgid ""
"Clicking on a post from a social media stream reveals a pop-up window, "
"showcasing the content of that specific post, along with all the engagement "
"data related to it (e.g. likes, comments, etc.)."
msgstr ""
"Mengklik postingan dari aliran media sosial akan menampilkan jendela pop-up, "
"menampilkan konten dari postingan tertentu tersebut, bersama dengan semua "
"data keterlibatan yang terkait dengannya (misalnya suka, komentar, dll.)."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/social_marketing/social_posts.rst:None
msgid ""
"Sample of a social media post's pop-up window in Odoo Social Marketing "
"application."
msgstr ""
"Contoh jendela pop-up postingan media sosial di aplikasi Odoo Social "
"Marketing."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/social_marketing/social_posts.rst:106
msgid ""
"If desired, the user can leave a new comment of the post from the post's pop-"
"up window, by typing one in the :guilabel:`Write a comment...` field, and "
"clicking :guilabel:`Enter` to post that comment."
msgstr ""
"Jika diinginkan, user dapat meninggalkan komentar baru pada postingan dari "
"jendela pop-up postingan, dengan mengetiknya di kolom :guilabel:`Tulis "
"komentar...`, dan mengklik :guilabel:`Enter` untuk memposting komentar "
"tersebut."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/social_marketing/social_posts.rst:111
msgid "Create leads from comments"
msgstr "Buat prospek dari komentar"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/social_marketing/social_posts.rst:113
msgid ""
"Odoo *Social Marketing* also provides the ability to create leads directly "
"from social media comments."
msgstr ""
"Odoo *Social Marketing* juga menyediakan kemampuan untuk membuat prospek "
"langsung dari komentar media sosial."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/social_marketing/social_posts.rst:116
msgid ""
"To create a lead from a comment left on a social media post, click on the "
"desired post from the dashboard to reveal that post's specific pop-up "
"window. Then, scroll to the desired comment, and click the :guilabel:`three "
"vertical dots` icon to the right of that comment."
msgstr ""
"Untuk membuat prospek dari komentar yang ditinggalkan pada posting media "
"sosial, klik posting yang diinginkan dari dashboard untuk menampilkan "
"jendela pop-up khusus posting tersebut. Kemudian, gulir ke komentar yang "
"diinginkan dan klik ikon :guilabel:`tiga titik vertikal` di sebelah kanan "
"komentar tersebut."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/social_marketing/social_posts.rst:120
msgid ""
"Doing so reveals a drop-down menu with the option: :guilabel:`Create Lead`."
msgstr ""
"Melakukan hal ini akan menampilkan menu drop-down dengan opsi: "
":guilabel:`Create Lead`."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/social_marketing/social_posts.rst:None
msgid ""
"The drop-down menu beside a comment revealing the option to create a lead."
msgstr ""
"Menu drop-down di samping komentar yang menampilkan opsi untuk membuat "
"prospek."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/social_marketing/social_posts.rst:126
msgid ""
"Upon clicking :guilabel:`Create Lead` from the comment's drop-down menu, "
"a :guilabel:`Conver Post to Lead` pop-up window appears."
msgstr ""
"Setelah mengklik :guilabel:`Create Lead` dari menu drop-down komentar, "
"jendela pop-up :guilabel:`Conver Post to Lead` akan muncul."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/social_marketing/social_posts.rst:None
msgid ""
"The convert post to lead pop-up window that appears in Odoo Social Marketing."
msgstr ""
"Jendela pop-up convert post to lead yang muncul di Odoo Social Marketing."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/social_marketing/social_posts.rst:133
msgid ""
"In this pop-up window, select to either: :guilabel:`Create a new "
"customer`, :guilabel:`Link to an existing customer`, or :guilabel:`Do not "
"link to a customer`."
msgstr ""
"Pada jendela pop-up ini, pilih salah satu: :guilabel:`Create a new "
"customer`, :guilabel:`Link to an existing customer`, atau :guilabel:`Do not "
"link to a customer`."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/social_marketing/social_posts.rst:137
msgid ""
"If :guilabel:`Link to an existing customer` is selected, a "
"new :guilabel:`Customer` field appears beneath those options, wherein a "
"customer can be chosen to be linked to this lead."
msgstr ""
"Jika :guilabel:`Link to an existing customer` dipilih, kolom "
":guilabel:`Customer` baru akan muncul di bawah opsi tersebut, di mana "
"pelanggan dapat dipilih untuk ditautkan ke prospek ini."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/social_marketing/social_posts.rst:140
msgid ""
"Once the desired selection has been made, click the :guilabel:`Convert` "
"button at the bottom of the :guilabel:`Convert Post to Lead` pop-up window. "
"Doing so reveals a fresh lead detail form, where the necessary information "
"can be entered and processed."
msgstr ""
"Setelah pilihan yang diinginkan dibuat, klik tombol :guilabel:`Convert` di "
"bagian bawah jendela pop-up :guilabel:`Convert Post to Lead`. Melakukan hal "
"ini akan menampilkan formulir detail prospek baru, di mana informasi yang "
"diperlukan dapat dimasukkan dan diproses."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/social_marketing/social_posts.rst:None
msgid ""
"New lead detail form generated from a social media comment in Odoo Social "
"Marketing."
msgstr ""
"Formulir detail prospek baru yang dibuat dari komentar media sosial di Odoo "
"Social Marketing."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/social_marketing/social_posts.rst:149
msgid "Insights"
msgstr "Insight"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/social_marketing/social_posts.rst:151
msgid ""
"When a social media account stream is added to the *Social Marketing* "
"dashboard, each stream also displays and links that specific social media "
"platform's KPIs (if the platform has them)."
msgstr ""
"Ketika stream akun media sosial ditambahkan ke Dashboard *Social Marketing*, "
"setiap stream juga menampilkan dan menautkan KPI platform media sosial "
"spesifik tersebut (jika platform memilikinya)."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/social_marketing/social_posts.rst:154
msgid ""
"To get redirected to the statistics and metrics related to any social media "
"account's KPIs, click on the :guilabel:`Insights` link, located at the top "
"of each stream."
msgstr ""
"Untuk dialihkan ke statistik dan metrik yang terkait dengan KPI akun media "
"sosial mana pun, klik tautan :guilabel:`Insights`, yang terletak di bagian "
"atas setiap stream."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/social_marketing/social_posts.rst:None
msgid ""
"Visual of how the Insights link appears on the dashboard of the Social "
"Marketing app."
msgstr ""
"Tampilan visual bagaimana tautan Insights muncul di Dashboard aplikasi "
"Social Marketing."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/social_marketing/social_posts.rst:162
msgid ""
"In a multi-company environment, if not *all* pages are selected, de-"
"authentication happens."
msgstr ""
"Dalam lingkungan multi-perusahaan, jika tidak *semua* halaman dipilih, de-"
"autentikasi terjadi."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/social_marketing/social_posts.rst:164
msgid ""
"For example, if the companies have 3 *Facebook* pages, but only grant access "
"to 1, and try to grant access to another at a later date, they will be de-"
"authenticated, and access to the initial page's insights/analytics will be "
"lost."
msgstr ""
"Misalnya, jika perusahaan memiliki 3 halaman *Facebook*, tetapi hanya "
"memberikan akses ke 1, dan mencoba memberikan akses ke halaman lain di "
"kemudian hari, mereka akan di-de-autentikasi, dan akses ke insights/analitik "
"halaman awal akan hilang."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/social_marketing/social_posts.rst:168
msgid ""
"So, be sure to add *all* pages for *all* companies in a multi-company "
"environment to avoid this issue. If a page gets de-autenticated, simply "
"remove the stream, and re-establish it."
msgstr ""
"Jadi, pastikan untuk menambahkan *semua* halaman untuk *semua* perusahaan "
"dalam lingkungan multi-perusahaan untuk menghindari masalah ini. Jika "
"halaman ter-de-autentikasi, cukup hapus stream, dan buat ulang."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/social_marketing/social_posts.rst:172
msgid "Create and post social media content"
msgstr "Buat dan posting konten media sosial"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/social_marketing/social_posts.rst:174
msgid ""
"Odoo *Social Marketing* offers the ability to create and post content for "
"social media accounts directly through the application."
msgstr ""
"Odoo *Social Marketing* menawarkan kemampuan untuk membuat dan memposting "
"konten untuk akun media sosial langsung melalui aplikasi."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/social_marketing/social_posts.rst:177
msgid ""
"To create content for social media accounts, navigated to "
"the :menuselection:`Social Marketing app`, and click :guilabel:`New Post` "
"located in the upper-right corner of the *Social Marketing* dashboard."
msgstr ""
"Untuk membuat konten untuk akun media sosial, navigasikan ke "
":menuselection:`aplikasi Social Marketing`, dan klik :guilabel:`New Post` "
"yang terletak di sudut kanan atas dashboard *Social Marketing*."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/social_marketing/social_posts.rst:None
msgid ""
"New Post button on the main dashboard of the Odoo Social Marketing "
"application."
msgstr "Tombol New Post di Dashboard utama aplikasi Odoo Social Marketing."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/social_marketing/social_posts.rst:185
msgid ""
"Or, navigate to :menuselection:`Social Marketing app --> Posts` and click "
"the :guilabel:`New` button."
msgstr ""
"Atau, buka :menuselection:`Social Marketing app --> Posts` dan klik tombol "
":guilabel:`New`."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/social_marketing/social_posts.rst:None
msgid ""
"New button on the Social Posts page in the Odoo Social Marketing application."
msgstr ""
"Tombol Baru di halaman Postingan Sosial dalam aplikasi Odoo Social Marketing."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/social_marketing/social_posts.rst:192
msgid ""
"Either route reveals a blank social media post detail form that can be "
"customized and configured in a number of different ways."
msgstr ""
"Kedua rute tersebut menampilkan formulir detail postingan media sosial "
"kosong yang dapat disesuaikan dan dikonfigurasi dengan berbagai cara."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/social_marketing/social_posts.rst:None
msgid "Blank social media post detail page in Odoo Social Marketing."
msgstr "Halaman detail postingan media sosial kosong di Odoo Social Marketing."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/social_marketing/social_posts.rst:200
msgid "Post detail form"
msgstr "Formulir detail postingan"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/social_marketing/social_posts.rst:202
msgid ""
"The social media post detail form in Odoo *Social Marketing* has many "
"different configurable options available."
msgstr ""
"Formulir detail postingan media sosial di Odoo *Social Marketing* memiliki "
"banyak opsi yang dapat dikonfigurasi."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/social_marketing/social_posts.rst:206
msgid "Company"
msgstr "Perusahaan"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/social_marketing/social_posts.rst:208
msgid ""
"If working in a multi-company environment, the first field in "
"the :guilabel:`Your Post` section of the social media post detail form "
"is :guilabel:`Company`. In this field, select the company that should be "
"connected to this specific social media post."
msgstr ""
"Jika bekerja dalam lingkungan multi-perusahaan, kolom pertama di bagian "
":guilabel:`Postingan Anda` pada formulir detail postingan media sosial "
"adalah :guilabel:`Perusahaan`. Di kolom ini, pilih perusahaan yang harus "
"dihubungkan dengan postingan media sosial tertentu ini."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/social_marketing/social_posts.rst:213
msgid "Post on"
msgstr "Post pada"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/social_marketing/social_posts.rst:215
msgid ""
"If working in a single-company environment, the first field in "
"the :guilabel:`Your Post` section of the social media post detail form "
"is :guilabel:`Post on`. In this field, determine which social media outlets "
"(streams) this post is intended to be posted on, and/or which website's "
"visitors this post should be sent to, via push notification, by checking the "
"box beside the desired option(s)."
msgstr ""
"Jika bekerja dalam lingkungan perusahaan tunggal, kolom pertama di bagian "
":guilabel:`Postingan Anda` pada formulir detail postingan media sosial "
"adalah :guilabel:`Posting di`. Di kolom ini, tentukan outlet media sosial "
"(stream) mana yang akan dijadikan tujuan postingan ini, dan/atau pengunjung "
"website mana yang akan menerima postingan ini melalui notifikasi push, "
"dengan mencentang kotak di samping opsi yang diinginkan."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/social_marketing/social_posts.rst:220
msgid ""
"Odoo automatically provides every available social media account that's been "
"linked to the database as an option in this section. If a social media "
"account hasn't been added as a stream to the *Social Marketing* application, "
"it will **not** appear as an option on the post template."
msgstr ""
"Odoo secara otomatis menyediakan setiap akun media sosial yang telah "
"ditautkan ke database sebagai opsi di bagian ini. Jika akun media sosial "
"belum ditambahkan sebagai stream ke aplikasi *Social Marketing*, akun "
"tersebut **tidak** akan muncul sebagai opsi pada template postingan."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/social_marketing/social_posts.rst:224
msgid ""
"Multiple social media outlets (streams) and websites can be selected in "
"the :guilabel:`Post on` field. At least **one** option in "
"the :guilabel:`Post on` field *must* be selected."
msgstr ""
"Beberapa outlet media sosial (stream) dan website dapat dipilih di kolom "
":guilabel:`Posting di`. Setidaknya **satu** opsi di kolom :guilabel:`Posting "
"di` *harus* dipilih."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/social_marketing/social_posts.rst:228
msgid ""
"In order for the :guilabel:`Push Notification` option to appear on the "
"social media post detail form in Odoo *Social Marketing*, make sure the "
"*Enable Web Push Notifications* feature is enabled in the *Website* app."
msgstr ""
"Agar opsi :guilabel:`Notifikasi Push` muncul pada formulir detail postingan "
"media sosial di Odoo *Social Marketing*, pastikan fitur *Enable Web Push "
"Notifications* diaktifkan di aplikasi *Website*."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/social_marketing/social_posts.rst:232
msgid ""
"To do that, navigate to :menuselection:`Website app --> Configuration --> "
"Settings`, activate :guilabel:`Enable Web Push Notifications`, fill out the "
"corresponding fields, and click :guilabel:`Save`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk melakukannya, buka :menuselection:`Aplikasi Website --> "
"Konfigurasi --> Pengaturan`, aktifkan :guilabel:`Enable Web Push "
"Notifications`, isi kolom yang sesuai, dan klik :guilabel:`Simpan`."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/social_marketing/social_posts.rst:237
msgid "Message"
msgstr "Pesan"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/social_marketing/social_posts.rst:239
msgid ""
"Next, there's the :guilabel:`Message` field. This is where the main content "
"of the post is created."
msgstr ""
"Selanjutnya, terdapat kolom :guilabel:`Pesan`. Di sinilah konten utama "
"postingan dibuat."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/social_marketing/social_posts.rst:241
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Message` field, type in the desired message for the social "
"post. After typing, click away from the :guilabel:`Message` field to reveal "
"visual samples of how the post will look on all the previously selected "
"social media accounts (and/or websites, as push notifications)."
msgstr ""
"Di kolom :guilabel:`Pesan`, ketik pesan yang diinginkan untuk postingan "
"sosial. Setelah mengetik, klik di luar kolom :guilabel:`Pesan` untuk "
"menampilkan sampel visual bagaimana postingan akan terlihat di semua akun "
"media sosial yang telah dipilih sebelumnya (dan/atau website, sebagai "
"notifikasi push)."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/social_marketing/social_posts.rst:None
msgid ""
"Sample social media post with visual samples of how it will appear on social "
"media outlets."
msgstr ""
"Sampel postingan media sosial dengan sampel visual bagaimana postingan akan "
"muncul di outlet media sosial."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/social_marketing/social_posts.rst:250
msgid ""
"Emojis can also be added directly to the text in the :guilabel:`Message` "
"field. Just click the :guilabel:`🙂 (smiley face)` icon, located on the line "
"of the :guilabel:`Message` field to the far right. Clicking this icon "
"reveals a drop-down menu containing numerous emojis to choose from."
msgstr ""
"Emoji juga dapat ditambahkan langsung ke teks di kolom :guilabel:`Pesan`. "
"Cukup klik ikon :guilabel:`🙂 (wajah senyum)`, yang terletak di baris kolom "
":guilabel:`Pesan` di sebelah kanan. Mengklik ikon ini menampilkan menu drop-"
"down yang berisi banyak emoji untuk dipilih."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/social_marketing/social_posts.rst:255
msgid ""
"If :guilabel:`Twitter` is chosen in the :guilabel:`Post on` field, a "
"character counter appears beneath the :guilabel:`Message` field."
msgstr ""
"Jika :guilabel:`Twitter` dipilih di kolom :guilabel:`Posting di`, penghitung "
"karakter muncul di bawah kolom :guilabel:`Pesan`."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/social_marketing/social_posts.rst:259
msgid "Attach Images"
msgstr "Lampirkan Gambar"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/social_marketing/social_posts.rst:261
msgid ""
"If images are to be used in the post, click the :guilabel:`Attach Images` "
"button, in the :guilabel:`Attach Images` field, located beneath "
"the :guilabel:`Message` field. When clicked, Odoo reveals a pop-up window. "
"In this pop-up window, select the desired image from the hard drive, and "
"upload it."
msgstr ""
"Jika gambar akan digunakan dalam postingan, klik tombol :guilabel:`Lampirkan "
"Gambar`, di kolom :guilabel:`Lampirkan Gambar`, yang terletak di bawah kolom "
":guilabel:`Pesan`. Saat diklik, Odoo menampilkan jendela pop-up. Di jendela "
"pop-up ini, pilih gambar yang diinginkan dari hard drive, dan unggah."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/social_marketing/social_posts.rst:266
msgid ""
"After successfully uploading and attaching the desired image, Odoo reveals a "
"new preview of the social media post, complete with the newly-added image, "
"on the right side of the detail form."
msgstr ""
"Setelah berhasil mengunggah dan melampirkan gambar yang diinginkan, Odoo "
"menampilkan pratinjau baru dari postingan media sosial, lengkap dengan "
"gambar yang baru ditambahkan, di sisi kanan formulir detail."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/social_marketing/social_posts.rst:None
msgid ""
"Visualized samples of post with newly-attached images in Odoo Social "
"Marketing."
msgstr ""
"Sampel tergambarkan dari postingan dengan gambar yang baru dilampirkan di "
"Odoo Social Marketing."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/social_marketing/social_posts.rst:274
msgid "Campaign"
msgstr "Kampanye"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/social_marketing/social_posts.rst:276
msgid ""
"Next, there is the :guilabel:`Campaign` field. This non-required field "
"provides the options to attach this post to a specific marketing campaign."
msgstr ""
"Selanjutnya, terdapat kolom :guilabel:`Kampanye`. Kolom yang tidak wajib "
"diisi ini menyediakan opsi untuk melampirkan postingan ini ke kampanye "
"pemasaran tertentu."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/social_marketing/social_posts.rst:279
msgid ""
"To add this post to a pre-existing campaign, click the "
"empty :guilabel:`Campaign` field to reveal a drop-down menu, containing all "
"the existing campaigns in the database. Select the desired campaign from "
"this drop-down menu to add this post to that campaign."
msgstr ""
"Untuk menambahkan postingan ini ke kampanye yang sudah ada, klik kolom "
":guilabel:`Campaign` yang kosong untuk menampilkan menu drop-down yang "
"berisi semua kampanye yang ada di database. Pilih kampanye yang diinginkan "
"dari menu drop-down ini untuk menambahkan postingan ini ke kampanye tersebut."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/social_marketing/social_posts.rst:283
msgid ""
"To create a new campaign directly from the social media post detail form, "
"start typing the name of the new campaign in the blank :guilabel:`Campaign` "
"field, and select either :guilabel:`Create` or :guilabel:`Create and "
"edit...`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk membuat kampanye baru langsung dari formulir detail postingan media "
"sosial, mulai ketik nama kampanye baru di bidang :guilabel:`Campaign` yang "
"kosong, dan pilih :guilabel:`Create` atau :guilabel:`Create and edit...`."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/social_marketing/social_posts.rst:None
msgid ""
"Drop-down menu options of Create or Create and edit in the Campaign field."
msgstr "Opsi menu drop-down Create atau Create and edit di kolom Campaign."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/social_marketing/social_posts.rst:291
msgid ""
"Clicking :guilabel:`Create` creates the campaign, which can be edited/"
"customized later."
msgstr ""
"Mengklik :guilabel:`Create` akan membuat kampanye yang dapat diedit/"
"disesuaikan nanti."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/social_marketing/social_posts.rst:293
msgid ""
"Clicking :guilabel:`Create and edit...` creates the campaign, and reveals "
"a :guilabel:`Create Campaign` pop-up form, wherein the :guilabel:`Campaign "
"Identifier`, :guilabel:`Responsible`, and :guilabel:`Tags` can be instantly "
"configured."
msgstr ""
"Mengklik :guilabel:`Create and edit...` akan membuat kampanye, dan "
"menampilkan formulir pop-up :guilabel:`Create Campaign`, di mana "
":guilabel:`Campaign Identifier`, :guilabel:`Responsible`, dan "
":guilabel:`Tags` dapat dikonfigurasi secara instan."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/social_marketing/social_posts.rst:None
msgid ""
"Create campaign pop-up window that appears on a social media post detail "
"form."
msgstr ""
"Jendela pop-up Create campaign yang muncul pada formulir detail postingan "
"media sosial."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/social_marketing/social_posts.rst:301
msgid ""
"When all the desired settings have been entered, click :guilabel:`Save & "
"Close` to save the campaign and return to the social media post detail form."
msgstr ""
"Setelah semua pengaturan yang diinginkan telah dimasukkan, klik "
":guilabel:`Save & Close` untuk menyimpan kampanye dan kembali ke formulir "
"detail postingan media sosial."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/social_marketing/social_posts.rst:305
msgid "When"
msgstr "Kapan"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/social_marketing/social_posts.rst:307
msgid ""
"Then, in the :guilabel:`When` field, choose either :guilabel:`Send Now` to "
"have Odoo publish the post immediately, or :guilabel:`Schedule later` to "
"have Odoo publish the post at a later date and time."
msgstr ""
"Kemudian, di kolom :guilabel:`When`, pilih :guilabel:`Send Now` agar Odoo "
"mempublikasikan postingan segera, atau :guilabel:`Schedule later` agar Odoo "
"mempublikasikan postingan pada tanggal dan waktu yang akan datang."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/social_marketing/social_posts.rst:311
msgid ""
"If :guilabel:`Schedule later` is selected, a new :guilabel:`Scheduled Date` "
"field appears. Clicking the empty field reveals a pop-up calendar, in which "
"a future date and time can be designated."
msgstr ""
"Jika :guilabel:`Schedule later` dipilih, kolom :guilabel:`Scheduled Date` "
"baru akan muncul. Mengklik kolom kosong tersebut akan menampilkan pop-up "
"kalender, di mana tanggal dan waktu yang akan datang dapat ditentukan."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/social_marketing/social_posts.rst:None
msgid ""
"Schedule date pop-up window that appears on social media post detail form in "
"Odoo."
msgstr ""
"Jendela pop-up Schedule date yang muncul pada formulir detail postingan "
"media sosial di Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/social_marketing/social_posts.rst:318
msgid ""
"After selecting a desired date and time, click :guilabel:`Apply`. Then, Odoo "
"will promptly publish the post at that specific date and time on the pre-"
"detemined social media account(s)."
msgstr ""
"Setelah memilih tanggal dan waktu yang diinginkan, klik :guilabel:`Apply`. "
"Kemudian, Odoo akan segera mempublikasikan postingan pada tanggal dan waktu "
"spesifik tersebut di akun media sosial yang telah ditentukan sebelumnya."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/social_marketing/social_posts.rst:322
msgid ""
"If scheduling a post, the :guilabel:`Post` button at the top of the social "
"media post detail form changes to :guilabel:`Schedule`. Be sure to "
"click :guilabel:`Schedule` after completing the social media post detail "
"form."
msgstr ""
"Jika menjadwalkan postingan, tombol :guilabel:`Post` di bagian atas formulir "
"detail postingan media sosial berubah menjadi :guilabel:`Schedule`. Pastikan "
"untuk mengklik :guilabel:`Schedule` setelah menyelesaikan formulir detail "
"postingan media sosial."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/social_marketing/social_posts.rst:326
msgid ""
"Doing so, locks in that specific date/time for Odoo to send the post, and it "
"changes the status of the post to :guilabel:`Scheduled`."
msgstr ""
"Dengan melakukan hal tersebut, tanggal/waktu tertentu untuk Odoo mengirim "
"postingan akan terkunci, dan status postingan berubah menjadi "
":guilabel:`Scheduled`."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/social_marketing/social_posts.rst:330
msgid "Push Notification Options"
msgstr "Opsi Push Notification"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/social_marketing/social_posts.rst:332
msgid ""
"If one (or multiple) :guilabel:`[Push Notification]` options are chosen in "
"the :guilabel:`Post on` field, a specific :guilabel:`Push Notification "
"Options` section appears at the bottom of the social media post detail form."
msgstr ""
"Jika satu (atau beberapa) opsi :guilabel:`[Push Notification]` dipilih di "
"kolom :guilabel:`Post on`, bagian :guilabel:`Push Notification Options` "
"khusus akan muncul di bagian bawah formulir detail postingan media sosial."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/social_marketing/social_posts.rst:None
msgid "Push notification options section on a social media post detail form."
msgstr ""
"Bagian push notification options pada formulir detail postingan media sosial."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/social_marketing/social_posts.rst:340
msgid "It should be noted that *none* of these fields are required."
msgstr "Perlu dicatat bahwa *tidak ada* kolom yang wajib diisi."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/social_marketing/social_posts.rst:342
msgid ""
"The first field in this section is :guilabel:`Notification Title`. In this "
"field, there is the option to add a custom title to the push notification "
"that will be sent."
msgstr ""
"Kolom pertama di bagian ini adalah :guilabel:`Notification Title`. Di kolom "
"ini, terdapat opsi untuk menambahkan judul khusus pada notifikasi push yang "
"akan dikirim."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/social_marketing/social_posts.rst:345
msgid ""
"To designate a specific page on the website that should trigger this push "
"notification, enter that page's URL in the :guilabel:`Target URL` field. "
"Then, once a visitor reaches that specific page, Odoo will display the push "
"notification."
msgstr ""
"Untuk menentukan halaman spesifik di website yang harus memicu notifikasi "
"push ini, masukkan URL halaman tersebut di bidang :guilabel:`Target URL`. "
"Kemudian, setelah pengunjung mencapai halaman spesifik tersebut, Odoo akan "
"menampilkan notifikasi push."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/social_marketing/social_posts.rst:349
msgid ""
"Below that field is the option to add a custom :guilabel:`Icon Image` to the "
"push notification. This is an icon that appears beside the push notification."
msgstr ""
"Di bawah kolom tersebut terdapat opsi untuk menambahkan :guilabel:`Icon "
"Image` khusus ke notifikasi push. Ini adalah ikon yang muncul di samping "
"notifikasi push."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/social_marketing/social_posts.rst:352
msgid ""
"To upload a new image, click the :guilabel:`✏️ (pencil) icon` when hovering "
"over the :guilabel:`Icon Image` camera icon. Doing so reveals a pop-up "
"window, in which the desired icon image can be located on the hard drive, "
"and subsequently uploaded."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mengunggah gambar baru, klik ikon :guilabel:`✏️ (pensil)` saat "
"mengarahkan kursor ke ikon kamera :guilabel:`Icon Image`. Melakukan hal ini "
"akan menampilkan jendela pop-up, di mana gambar ikon yang diinginkan dapat "
"ditemukan di hard drive, dan kemudian diunggah."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/social_marketing/social_posts.rst:356
msgid ""
"Once that's complete, Odoo automatically updates the visual preview of how "
"the icon appears on the push notification."
msgstr ""
"Setelah selesai, Odoo secara otomatis memperbarui pratinjau visual tentang "
"bagaimana ikon muncul pada notifikasi push."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/social_marketing/social_posts.rst:360
msgid ""
"Next, if the post is scheduled to be posted later, there is the option to "
"ensure the post is sent in the visitor's timezone, by enabling "
"the :guilabel:`Local Time` option. If enabled, Odoo will send it at the "
"appropriate, pre-determined time, taking the visitor's location into "
"consideration."
msgstr ""
"Selanjutnya, jika postingan dijadwalkan untuk diposting nanti, terdapat opsi "
"untuk memastikan postingan dikirim dalam zona waktu pengunjung, dengan "
"mengaktifkan opsi :guilabel:`Local Time`. Jika diaktifkan, Odoo akan "
"mengirimnya pada waktu yang tepat dan telah ditentukan sebelumnya, dengan "
"mempertimbangkan lokasi pengunjung."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/social_marketing/social_posts.rst:0
msgid ""
"The Local Time option in the Push Notification Options section of features."
msgstr "Opsi Local Time di bagian Push Notification Options."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/social_marketing/social_posts.rst:369
msgid ""
"Then, there is the :guilabel:`Match all records` field. This field provides "
"the ability to target a specific group of recipients in the database, based "
"on certain criteria, and can be applied to match :guilabel:`all` "
"or :guilabel:`any` of the rules."
msgstr ""
"Kemudian, terdapat kolom :guilabel:`Match all records`. Kolom ini "
"menyediakan kemampuan untuk menargetkan kelompok penerima tertentu di "
"database, berdasarkan kriteria tertentu, dan dapat diterapkan untuk "
"mencocokkan :guilabel:`all` atau :guilabel:`any` dari aturan."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/social_marketing/social_posts.rst:373
msgid ""
"To utilize this field, click the :guilabel:`+ Add condition` button, which "
"reveals an equation-like rule field."
msgstr ""
"Untuk menggunakan kolom ini, klik tombol :guilabel:`+ Add condition`, yang "
"akan menampilkan kolom aturan berbentuk persamaan."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/social_marketing/social_posts.rst:376
msgid ""
"In this equation-like rule field, specifiy the specific criteria Odoo should "
"take into account when sending this post to a particular target audience."
msgstr ""
"Dalam bidang aturan seperti persamaan ini, tentukan kriteria spesifik yang "
"harus dipertimbangkan Odoo saat mengirim postingan ini ke audiens target "
"tertentu."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/social_marketing/social_posts.rst:None
msgid ""
"Push notification conditions set up to match a specific amount of records in "
"the database."
msgstr ""
"Kondisi notifikasi push diatur untuk mencocokkan jumlah spesifik dari record "
"dalam database."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/social_marketing/social_posts.rst:383
msgid ""
"To add an additional rule, click the :guilabel:`➕ (plus sign) icon` to the "
"far-right of the rule."
msgstr ""
"Untuk menambahkan aturan tambahan, klik ikon :guilabel:`➕ (tanda plus)` di "
"sisi paling kanan aturan."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/social_marketing/social_posts.rst:385
msgid ""
"To add a branch (series of additional rules based on the previous rule, to "
"further specify a target audience), click the unique :guilabel:`branch "
"icon`, located to the right of the :guilabel:`➕ (plus sign) icon`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk menambahkan cabang (serangkaian aturan tambahan berdasarkan aturan "
"sebelumnya, untuk lebih menspesifikkan audiens target), klik :guilabel:`ikon "
"cabang` yang unik, terletak di sebelah kanan ikon :guilabel:`➕ (tanda plus)"
"`."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/social_marketing/social_posts.rst:389
msgid "Lastly, click the :guilabel:`🗑️ (trash can) icon` to delete any rule."
msgstr ""
"Terakhir, klik ikon :guilabel:`🗑️ (tempat sampah)` untuk menghapus aturan "
"apa pun."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/social_marketing/social_posts.rst:391
msgid ""
"The size of the specified target audience of recipients is represented by "
"the number of :guilabel:`Records` displayed beneath the rules."
msgstr ""
"Ukuran target audiens penerima yang ditentukan diwakili oleh jumlah "
":guilabel:`Record` yang ditampilkan di bawah aturan."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/social_marketing/social_posts.rst:395
msgid ":doc:`social_campaigns`"
msgstr ":doc:`social_campaigns`"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/surveys.rst:5
msgid "Surveys"
msgstr "Survei"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/surveys.rst:7
msgid ""
"Companies gather valuable insights from customers and employees through "
"surveys, aiding informed decision-making."
msgstr ""
"Perusahaan mengumpulkan wawasan berharga dari pelanggan dan karyawan melalui "
"survei, membantu pengambilan keputusan yang tepat."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/surveys.rst:10
msgid ""
"With Odoo *Surveys*, users create various surveys, questionnaires, "
"certifications, assessments, and so much more. These can be used to collect "
"feedback, evaluate the success of a recent event, and measure the "
"satisfaction of customers and/or employees. This process yields valuable "
"insights into shifting market trends."
msgstr ""
"Dengan Odoo *Survei*, pengguna membuat berbagai survei, kuesioner, "
"sertifikasi, penilaian, dan banyak lagi. Ini dapat digunakan untuk "
"mengumpulkan umpan balik, mengevaluasi kesuksesan acara terkini, dan "
"mengukur kepuasan pelanggan dan/atau karyawan. Proses ini menghasilkan "
"wawasan berharga tentang pergeseran tren pasar."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/surveys.rst:16
msgid "`Odoo Tutorials: Surveys <https://www.odoo.com/slides/surveys-62>`_"
msgstr "`Tutorial Odoo: Survei <https://www.odoo.com/slides/surveys-62>`_"

